   1277 </a><a href="#h3-0-141" id="h3-0-141" class="i">+	}
   1278 </a><a href="#h3-0-142" id="h3-0-142" class="i">+	float getIndirectIndex( const in int i ) {

   1283 </a><a href="#h3-0-147" id="h3-0-147" class="i">+	}

   1287 </a><a href="#h3-0-151" id="h3-0-151" class="i">+	vec3 getBatchingColor( const in float i ) {

   1302 </a><a href="#h3-0-166" id="h3-0-166" class="i">+#endif`,_F=`float G_BlinnPhong_Implicit( ) {
   1303 </a><a href="#h3-0-167" id="h3-0-167" class="i">+	return 0.25;
   1304 </a><a href="#h3-0-168" id="h3-0-168" class="i">+}
   1305 </a><a href="#h3-0-169" id="h3-0-169" class="i">+float D_BlinnPhong( const in float shininess, const in float dotNH ) {
   1306 </a><a href="#h3-0-170" id="h3-0-170" class="i">+	return RECIPROCAL_PI * ( shininess * 0.5 + 1.0 ) * pow( dotNH, shininess );
   1307 </a><a href="#h3-0-171" id="h3-0-171" class="i">+}
   1308 </a><a href="#h3-0-172" id="h3-0-172" class="i">+vec3 BRDF_BlinnPhong( const in vec3 lightDir, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 specularColor, const in float shininess ) {
   1309 </a><a href="#h3-0-173" id="h3-0-173" class="i">+	vec3 halfDir = normalize( lightDir + viewDir );
   1310 </a><a href="#h3-0-174" id="h3-0-174" class="i">+	float dotNH = saturate( dot( normal, halfDir ) );
   1311 </a><a href="#h3-0-175" id="h3-0-175" class="i">+	float dotVH = saturate( dot( viewDir, halfDir ) );
   1312 </a><a href="#h3-0-176" id="h3-0-176" class="i">+	vec3 F = F_Schlick( specularColor, 1.0, dotVH );
   1313 </a><a href="#h3-0-177" id="h3-0-177" class="i">+	float G = G_BlinnPhong_Implicit( );
   1314 </a><a href="#h3-0-178" id="h3-0-178" class="i">+	float D = D_BlinnPhong( shininess, dotNH );
   1315 </a><a href="#h3-0-179" id="h3-0-179" class="i">+	return F * ( G * D );
   1316 </a><a href="#h3-0-180" id="h3-0-180" class="i">+} // validated`,xF=`#ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   1317 </a><a href="#h3-0-181" id="h3-0-181" class="i">+	const mat3 XYZ_TO_REC709 = mat3(
   1318 </a><a href="#h3-0-182" id="h3-0-182" class="i">+		 3.2404542, -0.9692660,  0.0556434,
   1319 </a><a href="#h3-0-183" id="h3-0-183" class="i">+		-1.5371385,  1.8760108, -0.2040259,
   1320 </a><a href="#h3-0-184" id="h3-0-184" class="i">+		-0.4985314,  0.0415560,  1.0572252
   1321 </a><a href="#h3-0-185" id="h3-0-185" class="i">+	);
   1322 </a><a href="#h3-0-186" id="h3-0-186" class="i">+	vec3 Fresnel0ToIor( vec3 fresnel0 ) {
   1323 </a><a href="#h3-0-187" id="h3-0-187" class="i">+		vec3 sqrtF0 = sqrt( fresnel0 );
   1324 </a><a href="#h3-0-188" id="h3-0-188" class="i">+		return ( vec3( 1.0 ) + sqrtF0 ) / ( vec3( 1.0 ) - sqrtF0 );
   1325 </a><a href="#h3-0-189" id="h3-0-189" class="i">+	}
   1326 </a><a href="#h3-0-190" id="h3-0-190" class="i">+	vec3 IorToFresnel0( vec3 transmittedIor, float incidentIor ) {
   1327 </a><a href="#h3-0-191" id="h3-0-191" class="i">+		return pow2( ( transmittedIor - vec3( incidentIor ) ) / ( transmittedIor + vec3( incidentIor ) ) );
   1328 </a><a href="#h3-0-192" id="h3-0-192" class="i">+	}
   1329 </a><a href="#h3-0-193" id="h3-0-193" class="i">+	float IorToFresnel0( float transmittedIor, float incidentIor ) {
   1330 </a><a href="#h3-0-194" id="h3-0-194" class="i">+		return pow2( ( transmittedIor - incidentIor ) / ( transmittedIor + incidentIor ));
   1331 </a><a href="#h3-0-195" id="h3-0-195" class="i">+	}
   1332 </a><a href="#h3-0-196" id="h3-0-196" class="i">+	vec3 evalSensitivity( float OPD, vec3 shift ) {
   1333 </a><a href="#h3-0-197" id="h3-0-197" class="i">+		float phase = 2.0 * PI * OPD * 1.0e-9;
   1334 </a><a href="#h3-0-198" id="h3-0-198" class="i">+		vec3 val = vec3( 5.4856e-13, 4.4201e-13, 5.2481e-13 );
   1335 </a><a href="#h3-0-199" id="h3-0-199" class="i">+		vec3 pos = vec3( 1.6810e+06, 1.7953e+06, 2.2084e+06 );
   1336 </a><a href="#h3-0-200" id="h3-0-200" class="i">+		vec3 var = vec3( 4.3278e+09, 9.3046e+09, 6.6121e+09 );
   1337 </a><a href="#h3-0-201" id="h3-0-201" class="i">+		vec3 xyz = val * sqrt( 2.0 * PI * var ) * cos( pos * phase + shift ) * exp( - pow2( phase ) * var );
   1338 </a><a href="#h3-0-202" id="h3-0-202" class="i">+		xyz.x += 9.7470e-14 * sqrt( 2.0 * PI * 4.5282e+09 ) * cos( 2.2399e+06 * phase + shift[ 0 ] ) * exp( - 4.5282e+09 * pow2( phase ) );
   1339 </a><a href="#h3-0-203" id="h3-0-203" class="i">+		xyz /= 1.0685e-7;
   1340 </a><a href="#h3-0-204" id="h3-0-204" class="i">+		vec3 rgb = XYZ_TO_REC709 * xyz;
   1341 </a><a href="#h3-0-205" id="h3-0-205" class="i">+		return rgb;
   1342 </a><a href="#h3-0-206" id="h3-0-206" class="i">+	}
   1343 </a><a href="#h3-0-207" id="h3-0-207" class="i">+	vec3 evalIridescence( float outsideIOR, float eta2, float cosTheta1, float thinFilmThickness, vec3 baseF0 ) {
   1344 </a><a href="#h3-0-208" id="h3-0-208" class="i">+		vec3 I;
   1345 </a><a href="#h3-0-209" id="h3-0-209" class="i">+		float iridescenceIOR = mix( outsideIOR, eta2, smoothstep( 0.0, 0.03, thinFilmThickness ) );
   1346 </a><a href="#h3-0-210" id="h3-0-210" class="i">+		float sinTheta2Sq = pow2( outsideIOR / iridescenceIOR ) * ( 1.0 - pow2( cosTheta1 ) );
   1347 </a><a href="#h3-0-211" id="h3-0-211" class="i">+		float cosTheta2Sq = 1.0 - sinTheta2Sq;
   1348 </a><a href="#h3-0-212" id="h3-0-212" class="i">+		if ( cosTheta2Sq &lt; 0.0 ) {
   1349 </a><a href="#h3-0-213" id="h3-0-213" class="i">+			return vec3( 1.0 );
   1350 </a><a href="#h3-0-214" id="h3-0-214" class="i">+		}
   1351 </a><a href="#h3-0-215" id="h3-0-215" class="i">+		float cosTheta2 = sqrt( cosTheta2Sq );
   1352 </a><a href="#h3-0-216" id="h3-0-216" class="i">+		float R0 = IorToFresnel0( iridescenceIOR, outsideIOR );
   1353 </a><a href="#h3-0-217" id="h3-0-217" class="i">+		float R12 = F_Schlick( R0, 1.0, cosTheta1 );
   1354 </a><a href="#h3-0-218" id="h3-0-218" class="i">+		float T121 = 1.0 - R12;
   1355 </a><a href="#h3-0-219" id="h3-0-219" class="i">+		float phi12 = 0.0;
   1356 </a><a href="#h3-0-220" id="h3-0-220" class="i">+		if ( iridescenceIOR &lt; outsideIOR ) phi12 = PI;
   1357 </a><a href="#h3-0-221" id="h3-0-221" class="i">+		float phi21 = PI - phi12;
   1358 </a><a href="#h3-0-222" id="h3-0-222" class="i">+		vec3 baseIOR = Fresnel0ToIor( clamp( baseF0, 0.0, 0.9999 ) );		vec3 R1 = IorToFresnel0( baseIOR, iridescenceIOR );
   1359 </a><a href="#h3-0-223" id="h3-0-223" class="i">+		vec3 R23 = F_Schlick( R1, 1.0, cosTheta2 );
   1360 </a><a href="#h3-0-224" id="h3-0-224" class="i">+		vec3 phi23 = vec3( 0.0 );
   1361 </a><a href="#h3-0-225" id="h3-0-225" class="i">+		if ( baseIOR[ 0 ] &lt; iridescenceIOR ) phi23[ 0 ] = PI;
   1362 </a><a href="#h3-0-226" id="h3-0-226" class="i">+		if ( baseIOR[ 1 ] &lt; iridescenceIOR ) phi23[ 1 ] = PI;
   1363 </a><a href="#h3-0-227" id="h3-0-227" class="i">+		if ( baseIOR[ 2 ] &lt; iridescenceIOR ) phi23[ 2 ] = PI;
   1364 </a><a href="#h3-0-228" id="h3-0-228" class="i">+		float OPD = 2.0 * iridescenceIOR * thinFilmThickness * cosTheta2;
   1365 </a><a href="#h3-0-229" id="h3-0-229" class="i">+		vec3 phi = vec3( phi21 ) + phi23;
   1366 </a><a href="#h3-0-230" id="h3-0-230" class="i">+		vec3 R123 = clamp( R12 * R23, 1e-5, 0.9999 );
   1367 </a><a href="#h3-0-231" id="h3-0-231" class="i">+		vec3 r123 = sqrt( R123 );
   1368 </a><a href="#h3-0-232" id="h3-0-232" class="i">+		vec3 Rs = pow2( T121 ) * R23 / ( vec3( 1.0 ) - R123 );
   1369 </a><a href="#h3-0-233" id="h3-0-233" class="i">+		vec3 C0 = R12 + Rs;
   1370 </a><a href="#h3-0-234" id="h3-0-234" class="i">+		I = C0;
   1371 </a><a href="#h3-0-235" id="h3-0-235" class="i">+		vec3 Cm = Rs - T121;
   1372 </a><a href="#h3-0-236" id="h3-0-236" class="i">+		for ( int m = 1; m &lt;= 2; ++ m ) {
   1373 </a><a href="#h3-0-237" id="h3-0-237" class="i">+			Cm *= r123;
   1374 </a><a href="#h3-0-238" id="h3-0-238" class="i">+			vec3 Sm = 2.0 * evalSensitivity( float( m ) * OPD, float( m ) * phi );
   1375 </a><a href="#h3-0-239" id="h3-0-239" class="i">+			I += Cm * Sm;
   1376 </a><a href="#h3-0-240" id="h3-0-240" class="i">+		}
   1377 </a><a href="#h3-0-241" id="h3-0-241" class="i">+		return max( I, vec3( 0.0 ) );
   1378 </a><a href="#h3-0-242" id="h3-0-242" class="i">+	}
   1379 </a><a href="#h3-0-243" id="h3-0-243" class="i">+#endif`,SF=`#ifdef USE_BUMPMAP
   1380 </a><a href="#h3-0-244" id="h3-0-244" class="i">+	uniform sampler2D bumpMap;
   1381 </a><a href="#h3-0-245" id="h3-0-245" class="i">+	uniform float bumpScale;
   1382 </a><a href="#h3-0-246" id="h3-0-246" class="i">+	vec2 dHdxy_fwd() {
   1383 </a><a href="#h3-0-247" id="h3-0-247" class="i">+		vec2 dSTdx = dFdx( vBumpMapUv );
   1384 </a><a href="#h3-0-248" id="h3-0-248" class="i">+		vec2 dSTdy = dFdy( vBumpMapUv );
   1385 </a><a href="#h3-0-249" id="h3-0-249" class="i">+		float Hll = bumpScale * texture2D( bumpMap, vBumpMapUv ).x;
   1386 </a><a href="#h3-0-250" id="h3-0-250" class="i">+		float dBx = bumpScale * texture2D( bumpMap, vBumpMapUv + dSTdx ).x - Hll;
   1387 </a><a href="#h3-0-251" id="h3-0-251" class="i">+		float dBy = bumpScale * texture2D( bumpMap, vBumpMapUv + dSTdy ).x - Hll;
   1388 </a><a href="#h3-0-252" id="h3-0-252" class="i">+		return vec2( dBx, dBy );
   1389 </a><a href="#h3-0-253" id="h3-0-253" class="i">+	}
   1390 </a><a href="#h3-0-254" id="h3-0-254" class="i">+	vec3 perturbNormalArb( vec3 surf_pos, vec3 surf_norm, vec2 dHdxy, float faceDirection ) {
   1391 </a><a href="#h3-0-255" id="h3-0-255" class="i">+		vec3 vSigmaX = normalize( dFdx( surf_pos.xyz ) );
   1392 </a><a href="#h3-0-256" id="h3-0-256" class="i">+		vec3 vSigmaY = normalize( dFdy( surf_pos.xyz ) );
   1393 </a><a href="#h3-0-257" id="h3-0-257" class="i">+		vec3 vN = surf_norm;
   1394 </a><a href="#h3-0-258" id="h3-0-258" class="i">+		vec3 R1 = cross( vSigmaY, vN );
   1395 </a><a href="#h3-0-259" id="h3-0-259" class="i">+		vec3 R2 = cross( vN, vSigmaX );
   1396 </a><a href="#h3-0-260" id="h3-0-260" class="i">+		float fDet = dot( vSigmaX, R1 ) * faceDirection;
   1397 </a><a href="#h3-0-261" id="h3-0-261" class="i">+		vec3 vGrad = sign( fDet ) * ( dHdxy.x * R1 + dHdxy.y * R2 );
   1398 </a><a href="#h3-0-262" id="h3-0-262" class="i">+		return normalize( abs( fDet ) * surf_norm - vGrad );
   1399 </a><a href="#h3-0-263" id="h3-0-263" class="i">+	}
   1400 </a><a href="#h3-0-264" id="h3-0-264" class="i">+#endif`,MF=`#if NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES &gt; 0
   1401 </a><a href="#h3-0-265" id="h3-0-265" class="i">+	vec4 plane;
   1402 </a><a href="#h3-0-266" id="h3-0-266" class="i">+	#ifdef ALPHA_TO_COVERAGE
   1403 </a><a href="#h3-0-267" id="h3-0-267" class="i">+		float distanceToPlane, distanceGradient;
   1404 </a><a href="#h3-0-268" id="h3-0-268" class="i">+		float clipOpacity = 1.0;
   1405 </a><a href="#h3-0-269" id="h3-0-269" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_start
   1406 </a><a href="#h3-0-270" id="h3-0-270" class="i">+		for ( int i = 0; i &lt; UNION_CLIPPING_PLANES; i ++ ) {
   1407 </a><a href="#h3-0-271" id="h3-0-271" class="i">+			plane = clippingPlanes[ i ];
   1408 </a><a href="#h3-0-272" id="h3-0-272" class="i">+			distanceToPlane = - dot( vClipPosition, plane.xyz ) + plane.w;
   1409 </a><a href="#h3-0-273" id="h3-0-273" class="i">+			distanceGradient = fwidth( distanceToPlane ) / 2.0;
   1410 </a><a href="#h3-0-274" id="h3-0-274" class="i">+			clipOpacity *= smoothstep( - distanceGradient, distanceGradient, distanceToPlane );
   1411 </a><a href="#h3-0-275" id="h3-0-275" class="i">+			if ( clipOpacity == 0.0 ) discard;
   1412 </a><a href="#h3-0-276" id="h3-0-276" class="i">+		}
   1413 </a><a href="#h3-0-277" id="h3-0-277" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_end
   1414 </a><a href="#h3-0-278" id="h3-0-278" class="i">+		#if UNION_CLIPPING_PLANES &lt; NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES
   1415 </a><a href="#h3-0-279" id="h3-0-279" class="i">+			float unionClipOpacity = 1.0;
   1416 </a><a href="#h3-0-280" id="h3-0-280" class="i">+			#pragma unroll_loop_start
   1417 </a><a href="#h3-0-281" id="h3-0-281" class="i">+			for ( int i = UNION_CLIPPING_PLANES; i &lt; NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES; i ++ ) {
   1418 </a><a href="#h3-0-282" id="h3-0-282" class="i">+				plane = clippingPlanes[ i ];
   1419 </a><a href="#h3-0-283" id="h3-0-283" class="i">+				distanceToPlane = - dot( vClipPosition, plane.xyz ) + plane.w;
   1420 </a><a href="#h3-0-284" id="h3-0-284" class="i">+				distanceGradient = fwidth( distanceToPlane ) / 2.0;
   1421 </a><a href="#h3-0-285" id="h3-0-285" class="i">+				unionClipOpacity *= 1.0 - smoothstep( - distanceGradient, distanceGradient, distanceToPlane );
   1422 </a><a href="#h3-0-286" id="h3-0-286" class="i">+			}
   1423 </a><a href="#h3-0-287" id="h3-0-287" class="i">+			#pragma unroll_loop_end
   1424 </a><a href="#h3-0-288" id="h3-0-288" class="i">+			clipOpacity *= 1.0 - unionClipOpacity;
   1425 </a><a href="#h3-0-289" id="h3-0-289" class="i">+		#endif
   1426 </a><a href="#h3-0-290" id="h3-0-290" class="i">+		diffuseColor.a *= clipOpacity;
   1427 </a><a href="#h3-0-291" id="h3-0-291" class="i">+		if ( diffuseColor.a == 0.0 ) discard;
   1428 </a><a href="#h3-0-292" id="h3-0-292" class="i">+	#else
   1429 </a><a href="#h3-0-293" id="h3-0-293" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_start
   1430 </a><a href="#h3-0-294" id="h3-0-294" class="i">+		for ( int i = 0; i &lt; UNION_CLIPPING_PLANES; i ++ ) {
   1431 </a><a href="#h3-0-295" id="h3-0-295" class="i">+			plane = clippingPlanes[ i ];
   1432 </a><a href="#h3-0-296" id="h3-0-296" class="i">+			if ( dot( vClipPosition, plane.xyz ) &gt; plane.w ) discard;
   1433 </a><a href="#h3-0-297" id="h3-0-297" class="i">+		}
   1434 </a><a href="#h3-0-298" id="h3-0-298" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_end
   1435 </a><a href="#h3-0-299" id="h3-0-299" class="i">+		#if UNION_CLIPPING_PLANES &lt; NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES
   1436 </a><a href="#h3-0-300" id="h3-0-300" class="i">+			bool clipped = true;
   1437 </a><a href="#h3-0-301" id="h3-0-301" class="i">+			#pragma unroll_loop_start
   1438 </a><a href="#h3-0-302" id="h3-0-302" class="i">+			for ( int i = UNION_CLIPPING_PLANES; i &lt; NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES; i ++ ) {
   1439 </a><a href="#h3-0-303" id="h3-0-303" class="i">+				plane = clippingPlanes[ i ];
   1440 </a><a href="#h3-0-304" id="h3-0-304" class="i">+				clipped = ( dot( vClipPosition, plane.xyz ) &gt; plane.w ) &amp;&amp; clipped;
   1441 </a><a href="#h3-0-305" id="h3-0-305" class="i">+			}
   1442 </a><a href="#h3-0-306" id="h3-0-306" class="i">+			#pragma unroll_loop_end
   1443 </a><a href="#h3-0-307" id="h3-0-307" class="i">+			if ( clipped ) discard;
   1444 </a><a href="#h3-0-308" id="h3-0-308" class="i">+		#endif
   1445 </a><a href="#h3-0-309" id="h3-0-309" class="i">+	#endif
   1446 </a><a href="#h3-0-310" id="h3-0-310" class="i">+#endif`,EF=`#if NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES &gt; 0

   1449 </a><a href="#h3-0-313" id="h3-0-313" class="i">+#endif`,bF=`#if NUM_CLIPPING_PLANES &gt; 0

   1479 </a><a href="#h3-0-343" id="h3-0-343" class="i">+#endif`,DF=`#define PI 3.141592653589793
   1480 </a><a href="#h3-0-344" id="h3-0-344" class="i">+#define PI2 6.283185307179586

   1482 </a><a href="#h3-0-346" id="h3-0-346" class="i">+#define RECIPROCAL_PI 0.3183098861837907
   1483 </a><a href="#h3-0-347" id="h3-0-347" class="i">+#define RECIPROCAL_PI2 0.15915494309189535
   1484 </a><a href="#h3-0-348" id="h3-0-348" class="i">+#define EPSILON 1e-6
   1485 </a><a href="#h3-0-349" id="h3-0-349" class="i">+#ifndef saturate
   1486 </a><a href="#h3-0-350" id="h3-0-350" class="i">+#define saturate( a ) clamp( a, 0.0, 1.0 )

   1488 </a><a href="#h3-0-352" id="h3-0-352" class="i">+#define whiteComplement( a ) ( 1.0 - saturate( a ) )
   1489 </a><a href="#h3-0-353" id="h3-0-353" class="i">+float pow2( const in float x ) { return x*x; }
   1490 </a><a href="#h3-0-354" id="h3-0-354" class="i">+vec3 pow2( const in vec3 x ) { return x*x; }

   1492 </a><a href="#h3-0-356" id="h3-0-356" class="i">+float pow4( const in float x ) { float x2 = x*x; return x2*x2; }
   1493 </a><a href="#h3-0-357" id="h3-0-357" class="i">+float max3( const in vec3 v ) { return max( max( v.x, v.y ), v.z ); }
   1494 </a><a href="#h3-0-358" id="h3-0-358" class="i">+float average( const in vec3 v ) { return dot( v, vec3( 0.3333333 ) ); }
   1495 </a><a href="#h3-0-359" id="h3-0-359" class="i">+highp float rand( const in vec2 uv ) {
   1496 </a><a href="#h3-0-360" id="h3-0-360" class="i">+	const highp float a = 12.9898, b = 78.233, c = 43758.5453;
   1497 </a><a href="#h3-0-361" id="h3-0-361" class="i">+	highp float dt = dot( uv.xy, vec2( a,b ) ), sn = mod( dt, PI );
   1498 </a><a href="#h3-0-362" id="h3-0-362" class="i">+	return fract( sin( sn ) * c );
   1499 </a><a href="#h3-0-363" id="h3-0-363" class="i">+}
   1500 </a><a href="#h3-0-364" id="h3-0-364" class="i">+#ifdef HIGH_PRECISION
   1501 </a><a href="#h3-0-365" id="h3-0-365" class="i">+	float precisionSafeLength( vec3 v ) { return length( v ); }
   1502 </a><a href="#h3-0-366" id="h3-0-366" class="i">+#else
   1503 </a><a href="#h3-0-367" id="h3-0-367" class="i">+	float precisionSafeLength( vec3 v ) {
   1504 </a><a href="#h3-0-368" id="h3-0-368" class="i">+		float maxComponent = max3( abs( v ) );
   1505 </a><a href="#h3-0-369" id="h3-0-369" class="i">+		return length( v / maxComponent ) * maxComponent;
   1506 </a><a href="#h3-0-370" id="h3-0-370" class="i">+	}
   1507 </a><a href="#h3-0-371" id="h3-0-371" class="i">+#endif
   1508 </a><a href="#h3-0-372" id="h3-0-372" class="i">+struct IncidentLight {

   1510 </a><a href="#h3-0-374" id="h3-0-374" class="i">+	vec3 direction;

   1513 </a><a href="#h3-0-377" id="h3-0-377" class="i">+struct ReflectedLight {
   1514 </a><a href="#h3-0-378" id="h3-0-378" class="i">+	vec3 directDiffuse;

   1519 </a><a href="#h3-0-383" id="h3-0-383" class="i">+#ifdef USE_ALPHAHASH
   1520 </a><a href="#h3-0-384" id="h3-0-384" class="i">+	varying vec3 vPosition;
   1521 </a><a href="#h3-0-385" id="h3-0-385" class="i">+#endif
   1522 </a><a href="#h3-0-386" id="h3-0-386" class="i">+vec3 transformDirection( in vec3 dir, in mat4 matrix ) {
   1523 </a><a href="#h3-0-387" id="h3-0-387" class="i">+	return normalize( ( matrix * vec4( dir, 0.0 ) ).xyz );
   1524 </a><a href="#h3-0-388" id="h3-0-388" class="i">+}
   1525 </a><a href="#h3-0-389" id="h3-0-389" class="i">+vec3 inverseTransformDirection( in vec3 dir, in mat4 matrix ) {
   1526 </a><a href="#h3-0-390" id="h3-0-390" class="i">+	return normalize( ( vec4( dir, 0.0 ) * matrix ).xyz );
   1527 </a><a href="#h3-0-391" id="h3-0-391" class="i">+}
   1528 </a><a href="#h3-0-392" id="h3-0-392" class="i">+mat3 transposeMat3( const in mat3 m ) {
   1529 </a><a href="#h3-0-393" id="h3-0-393" class="i">+	mat3 tmp;
   1530 </a><a href="#h3-0-394" id="h3-0-394" class="i">+	tmp[ 0 ] = vec3( m[ 0 ].x, m[ 1 ].x, m[ 2 ].x );
   1531 </a><a href="#h3-0-395" id="h3-0-395" class="i">+	tmp[ 1 ] = vec3( m[ 0 ].y, m[ 1 ].y, m[ 2 ].y );
   1532 </a><a href="#h3-0-396" id="h3-0-396" class="i">+	tmp[ 2 ] = vec3( m[ 0 ].z, m[ 1 ].z, m[ 2 ].z );
   1533 </a><a href="#h3-0-397" id="h3-0-397" class="i">+	return tmp;
   1534 </a><a href="#h3-0-398" id="h3-0-398" class="i">+}
   1535 </a><a href="#h3-0-399" id="h3-0-399" class="i">+bool isPerspectiveMatrix( mat4 m ) {
   1536 </a><a href="#h3-0-400" id="h3-0-400" class="i">+	return m[ 2 ][ 3 ] == - 1.0;
   1537 </a><a href="#h3-0-401" id="h3-0-401" class="i">+}
   1538 </a><a href="#h3-0-402" id="h3-0-402" class="i">+vec2 equirectUv( in vec3 dir ) {
   1539 </a><a href="#h3-0-403" id="h3-0-403" class="i">+	float u = atan( dir.z, dir.x ) * RECIPROCAL_PI2 + 0.5;
   1540 </a><a href="#h3-0-404" id="h3-0-404" class="i">+	float v = asin( clamp( dir.y, - 1.0, 1.0 ) ) * RECIPROCAL_PI + 0.5;
   1541 </a><a href="#h3-0-405" id="h3-0-405" class="i">+	return vec2( u, v );
   1542 </a><a href="#h3-0-406" id="h3-0-406" class="i">+}
   1543 </a><a href="#h3-0-407" id="h3-0-407" class="i">+vec3 BRDF_Lambert( const in vec3 diffuseColor ) {
   1544 </a><a href="#h3-0-408" id="h3-0-408" class="i">+	return RECIPROCAL_PI * diffuseColor;
   1545 </a><a href="#h3-0-409" id="h3-0-409" class="i">+}
   1546 </a><a href="#h3-0-410" id="h3-0-410" class="i">+vec3 F_Schlick( const in vec3 f0, const in float f90, const in float dotVH ) {
   1547 </a><a href="#h3-0-411" id="h3-0-411" class="i">+	float fresnel = exp2( ( - 5.55473 * dotVH - 6.98316 ) * dotVH );
   1548 </a><a href="#h3-0-412" id="h3-0-412" class="i">+	return f0 * ( 1.0 - fresnel ) + ( f90 * fresnel );
   1549 </a><a href="#h3-0-413" id="h3-0-413" class="i">+}
   1550 </a><a href="#h3-0-414" id="h3-0-414" class="i">+float F_Schlick( const in float f0, const in float f90, const in float dotVH ) {
   1551 </a><a href="#h3-0-415" id="h3-0-415" class="i">+	float fresnel = exp2( ( - 5.55473 * dotVH - 6.98316 ) * dotVH );
   1552 </a><a href="#h3-0-416" id="h3-0-416" class="i">+	return f0 * ( 1.0 - fresnel ) + ( f90 * fresnel );
   1553 </a><a href="#h3-0-417" id="h3-0-417" class="i">+} // validated`,UF=`#ifdef ENVMAP_TYPE_CUBE_UV
   1554 </a><a href="#h3-0-418" id="h3-0-418" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_minMipLevel 4.0
   1555 </a><a href="#h3-0-419" id="h3-0-419" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_minTileSize 16.0
   1556 </a><a href="#h3-0-420" id="h3-0-420" class="i">+	float getFace( vec3 direction ) {
   1557 </a><a href="#h3-0-421" id="h3-0-421" class="i">+		vec3 absDirection = abs( direction );
   1558 </a><a href="#h3-0-422" id="h3-0-422" class="i">+		float face = - 1.0;
   1559 </a><a href="#h3-0-423" id="h3-0-423" class="i">+		if ( absDirection.x &gt; absDirection.z ) {
   1560 </a><a href="#h3-0-424" id="h3-0-424" class="i">+			if ( absDirection.x &gt; absDirection.y )
   1561 </a><a href="#h3-0-425" id="h3-0-425" class="i">+				face = direction.x &gt; 0.0 ? 0.0 : 3.0;
   1562 </a><a href="#h3-0-426" id="h3-0-426" class="i">+			else
   1563 </a><a href="#h3-0-427" id="h3-0-427" class="i">+				face = direction.y &gt; 0.0 ? 1.0 : 4.0;
   1564 </a><a href="#h3-0-428" id="h3-0-428" class="i">+		} else {
   1565 </a><a href="#h3-0-429" id="h3-0-429" class="i">+			if ( absDirection.z &gt; absDirection.y )
   1566 </a><a href="#h3-0-430" id="h3-0-430" class="i">+				face = direction.z &gt; 0.0 ? 2.0 : 5.0;
   1567 </a><a href="#h3-0-431" id="h3-0-431" class="i">+			else
   1568 </a><a href="#h3-0-432" id="h3-0-432" class="i">+				face = direction.y &gt; 0.0 ? 1.0 : 4.0;
   1569 </a><a href="#h3-0-433" id="h3-0-433" class="i">+		}
   1570 </a><a href="#h3-0-434" id="h3-0-434" class="i">+		return face;
   1571 </a><a href="#h3-0-435" id="h3-0-435" class="i">+	}
   1572 </a><a href="#h3-0-436" id="h3-0-436" class="i">+	vec2 getUV( vec3 direction, float face ) {
   1573 </a><a href="#h3-0-437" id="h3-0-437" class="i">+		vec2 uv;
   1574 </a><a href="#h3-0-438" id="h3-0-438" class="i">+		if ( face == 0.0 ) {
   1575 </a><a href="#h3-0-439" id="h3-0-439" class="i">+			uv = vec2( direction.z, direction.y ) / abs( direction.x );
   1576 </a><a href="#h3-0-440" id="h3-0-440" class="i">+		} else if ( face == 1.0 ) {
   1577 </a><a href="#h3-0-441" id="h3-0-441" class="i">+			uv = vec2( - direction.x, - direction.z ) / abs( direction.y );
   1578 </a><a href="#h3-0-442" id="h3-0-442" class="i">+		} else if ( face == 2.0 ) {
   1579 </a><a href="#h3-0-443" id="h3-0-443" class="i">+			uv = vec2( - direction.x, direction.y ) / abs( direction.z );
   1580 </a><a href="#h3-0-444" id="h3-0-444" class="i">+		} else if ( face == 3.0 ) {
   1581 </a><a href="#h3-0-445" id="h3-0-445" class="i">+			uv = vec2( - direction.z, direction.y ) / abs( direction.x );
   1582 </a><a href="#h3-0-446" id="h3-0-446" class="i">+		} else if ( face == 4.0 ) {
   1583 </a><a href="#h3-0-447" id="h3-0-447" class="i">+			uv = vec2( - direction.x, direction.z ) / abs( direction.y );
   1584 </a><a href="#h3-0-448" id="h3-0-448" class="i">+		} else {
   1585 </a><a href="#h3-0-449" id="h3-0-449" class="i">+			uv = vec2( direction.x, direction.y ) / abs( direction.z );
   1586 </a><a href="#h3-0-450" id="h3-0-450" class="i">+		}
   1587 </a><a href="#h3-0-451" id="h3-0-451" class="i">+		return 0.5 * ( uv + 1.0 );
   1588 </a><a href="#h3-0-452" id="h3-0-452" class="i">+	}
   1589 </a><a href="#h3-0-453" id="h3-0-453" class="i">+	vec3 bilinearCubeUV( sampler2D envMap, vec3 direction, float mipInt ) {
   1590 </a><a href="#h3-0-454" id="h3-0-454" class="i">+		float face = getFace( direction );
   1591 </a><a href="#h3-0-455" id="h3-0-455" class="i">+		float filterInt = max( cubeUV_minMipLevel - mipInt, 0.0 );
   1592 </a><a href="#h3-0-456" id="h3-0-456" class="i">+		mipInt = max( mipInt, cubeUV_minMipLevel );
   1593 </a><a href="#h3-0-457" id="h3-0-457" class="i">+		float faceSize = exp2( mipInt );
   1594 </a><a href="#h3-0-458" id="h3-0-458" class="i">+		highp vec2 uv = getUV( direction, face ) * ( faceSize - 2.0 ) + 1.0;
   1595 </a><a href="#h3-0-459" id="h3-0-459" class="i">+		if ( face &gt; 2.0 ) {
   1596 </a><a href="#h3-0-460" id="h3-0-460" class="i">+			uv.y += faceSize;
   1597 </a><a href="#h3-0-461" id="h3-0-461" class="i">+			face -= 3.0;
   1598 </a><a href="#h3-0-462" id="h3-0-462" class="i">+		}
   1599 </a><a href="#h3-0-463" id="h3-0-463" class="i">+		uv.x += face * faceSize;
   1600 </a><a href="#h3-0-464" id="h3-0-464" class="i">+		uv.x += filterInt * 3.0 * cubeUV_minTileSize;
   1601 </a><a href="#h3-0-465" id="h3-0-465" class="i">+		uv.y += 4.0 * ( exp2( CUBEUV_MAX_MIP ) - faceSize );
   1602 </a><a href="#h3-0-466" id="h3-0-466" class="i">+		uv.x *= CUBEUV_TEXEL_WIDTH;
   1603 </a><a href="#h3-0-467" id="h3-0-467" class="i">+		uv.y *= CUBEUV_TEXEL_HEIGHT;
   1604 </a><a href="#h3-0-468" id="h3-0-468" class="i">+		#ifdef texture2DGradEXT
   1605 </a><a href="#h3-0-469" id="h3-0-469" class="i">+			return texture2DGradEXT( envMap, uv, vec2( 0.0 ), vec2( 0.0 ) ).rgb;
   1606 </a><a href="#h3-0-470" id="h3-0-470" class="i">+		#else
   1607 </a><a href="#h3-0-471" id="h3-0-471" class="i">+			return texture2D( envMap, uv ).rgb;
   1608 </a><a href="#h3-0-472" id="h3-0-472" class="i">+		#endif
   1609 </a><a href="#h3-0-473" id="h3-0-473" class="i">+	}
   1610 </a><a href="#h3-0-474" id="h3-0-474" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_r0 1.0
   1611 </a><a href="#h3-0-475" id="h3-0-475" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_m0 - 2.0
   1612 </a><a href="#h3-0-476" id="h3-0-476" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_r1 0.8
   1613 </a><a href="#h3-0-477" id="h3-0-477" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_m1 - 1.0
   1614 </a><a href="#h3-0-478" id="h3-0-478" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_r4 0.4
   1615 </a><a href="#h3-0-479" id="h3-0-479" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_m4 2.0
   1616 </a><a href="#h3-0-480" id="h3-0-480" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_r5 0.305
   1617 </a><a href="#h3-0-481" id="h3-0-481" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_m5 3.0
   1618 </a><a href="#h3-0-482" id="h3-0-482" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_r6 0.21
   1619 </a><a href="#h3-0-483" id="h3-0-483" class="i">+	#define cubeUV_m6 4.0
   1620 </a><a href="#h3-0-484" id="h3-0-484" class="i">+	float roughnessToMip( float roughness ) {
   1621 </a><a href="#h3-0-485" id="h3-0-485" class="i">+		float mip = 0.0;
   1622 </a><a href="#h3-0-486" id="h3-0-486" class="i">+		if ( roughness &gt;= cubeUV_r1 ) {
   1623 </a><a href="#h3-0-487" id="h3-0-487" class="i">+			mip = ( cubeUV_r0 - roughness ) * ( cubeUV_m1 - cubeUV_m0 ) / ( cubeUV_r0 - cubeUV_r1 ) + cubeUV_m0;
   1624 </a><a href="#h3-0-488" id="h3-0-488" class="i">+		} else if ( roughness &gt;= cubeUV_r4 ) {
   1625 </a><a href="#h3-0-489" id="h3-0-489" class="i">+			mip = ( cubeUV_r1 - roughness ) * ( cubeUV_m4 - cubeUV_m1 ) / ( cubeUV_r1 - cubeUV_r4 ) + cubeUV_m1;
   1626 </a><a href="#h3-0-490" id="h3-0-490" class="i">+		} else if ( roughness &gt;= cubeUV_r5 ) {
   1627 </a><a href="#h3-0-491" id="h3-0-491" class="i">+			mip = ( cubeUV_r4 - roughness ) * ( cubeUV_m5 - cubeUV_m4 ) / ( cubeUV_r4 - cubeUV_r5 ) + cubeUV_m4;
   1628 </a><a href="#h3-0-492" id="h3-0-492" class="i">+		} else if ( roughness &gt;= cubeUV_r6 ) {
   1629 </a><a href="#h3-0-493" id="h3-0-493" class="i">+			mip = ( cubeUV_r5 - roughness ) * ( cubeUV_m6 - cubeUV_m5 ) / ( cubeUV_r5 - cubeUV_r6 ) + cubeUV_m5;
   1630 </a><a href="#h3-0-494" id="h3-0-494" class="i">+		} else {
   1631 </a><a href="#h3-0-495" id="h3-0-495" class="i">+			mip = - 2.0 * log2( 1.16 * roughness );		}
   1632 </a><a href="#h3-0-496" id="h3-0-496" class="i">+		return mip;
   1633 </a><a href="#h3-0-497" id="h3-0-497" class="i">+	}
   1634 </a><a href="#h3-0-498" id="h3-0-498" class="i">+	vec4 textureCubeUV( sampler2D envMap, vec3 sampleDir, float roughness ) {
   1635 </a><a href="#h3-0-499" id="h3-0-499" class="i">+		float mip = clamp( roughnessToMip( roughness ), cubeUV_m0, CUBEUV_MAX_MIP );
   1636 </a><a href="#h3-0-500" id="h3-0-500" class="i">+		float mipF = fract( mip );
   1637 </a><a href="#h3-0-501" id="h3-0-501" class="i">+		float mipInt = floor( mip );
   1638 </a><a href="#h3-0-502" id="h3-0-502" class="i">+		vec3 color0 = bilinearCubeUV( envMap, sampleDir, mipInt );
   1639 </a><a href="#h3-0-503" id="h3-0-503" class="i">+		if ( mipF == 0.0 ) {
   1640 </a><a href="#h3-0-504" id="h3-0-504" class="i">+			return vec4( color0, 1.0 );
   1641 </a><a href="#h3-0-505" id="h3-0-505" class="i">+		} else {
   1642 </a><a href="#h3-0-506" id="h3-0-506" class="i">+			vec3 color1 = bilinearCubeUV( envMap, sampleDir, mipInt + 1.0 );
   1643 </a><a href="#h3-0-507" id="h3-0-507" class="i">+			return vec4( mix( color0, color1, mipF ), 1.0 );
   1644 </a><a href="#h3-0-508" id="h3-0-508" class="i">+		}
   1645 </a><a href="#h3-0-509" id="h3-0-509" class="i">+	}
   1646 </a><a href="#h3-0-510" id="h3-0-510" class="i">+#endif`,NF=`vec3 transformedNormal = objectNormal;
   1647 </a><a href="#h3-0-511" id="h3-0-511" class="i">+#ifdef USE_TANGENT
   1648 </a><a href="#h3-0-512" id="h3-0-512" class="i">+	vec3 transformedTangent = objectTangent;
   1649 </a><a href="#h3-0-513" id="h3-0-513" class="i">+#endif
   1650 </a><a href="#h3-0-514" id="h3-0-514" class="i">+#ifdef USE_BATCHING

   1652 </a><a href="#h3-0-516" id="h3-0-516" class="i">+	transformedNormal /= vec3( dot( bm[ 0 ], bm[ 0 ] ), dot( bm[ 1 ], bm[ 1 ] ), dot( bm[ 2 ], bm[ 2 ] ) );

   1658 </a><a href="#h3-0-522" id="h3-0-522" class="i">+#ifdef USE_INSTANCING

   1676 </a><a href="#h3-0-540" id="h3-0-540" class="i">+	uniform sampler2D displacementMap;

   1678 </a><a href="#h3-0-542" id="h3-0-542" class="i">+	uniform float displacementBias;

   1692 </a><a href="#h3-0-556" id="h3-0-556" class="i">+vec4 sRGBTransferEOTF( in vec4 value ) {
   1693 </a><a href="#h3-0-557" id="h3-0-557" class="i">+	return vec4( mix( pow( value.rgb * 0.9478672986 + vec3( 0.0521327014 ), vec3( 2.4 ) ), value.rgb * 0.0773993808, vec3( lessThanEqual( value.rgb, vec3( 0.04045 ) ) ) ), value.a );
   1694 </a><a href="#h3-0-558" id="h3-0-558" class="i">+}
   1695 </a><a href="#h3-0-559" id="h3-0-559" class="i">+vec4 sRGBTransferOETF( in vec4 value ) {
   1696 </a><a href="#h3-0-560" id="h3-0-560" class="i">+	return vec4( mix( pow( value.rgb, vec3( 0.41666 ) ) * 1.055 - vec3( 0.055 ), value.rgb * 12.92, vec3( lessThanEqual( value.rgb, vec3( 0.0031308 ) ) ) ), value.a );

   1799 </a><a href="#h3-0-663" id="h3-0-663" class="i">+	float dotNL = dot( normal, lightDirection );
   1800 </a><a href="#h3-0-664" id="h3-0-664" class="i">+	vec2 coord = vec2( dotNL * 0.5 + 0.5, 0.0 );
   1801 </a><a href="#h3-0-665" id="h3-0-665" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_GRADIENTMAP
   1802 </a><a href="#h3-0-666" id="h3-0-666" class="i">+		return vec3( texture2D( gradientMap, coord ).r );
   1803 </a><a href="#h3-0-667" id="h3-0-667" class="i">+	#else
   1804 </a><a href="#h3-0-668" id="h3-0-668" class="i">+		vec2 fw = fwidth( coord ) * 0.5;
   1805 </a><a href="#h3-0-669" id="h3-0-669" class="i">+		return mix( vec3( 0.7 ), vec3( 1.0 ), smoothstep( 0.7 - fw.x, 0.7 + fw.x, coord.x ) );
   1806 </a><a href="#h3-0-670" id="h3-0-670" class="i">+	#endif
   1807 </a><a href="#h3-0-671" id="h3-0-671" class="i">+}`,jF=`#ifdef USE_LIGHTMAP
   1808 </a><a href="#h3-0-672" id="h3-0-672" class="i">+	uniform sampler2D lightMap;
   1809 </a><a href="#h3-0-673" id="h3-0-673" class="i">+	uniform float lightMapIntensity;
   1810 </a><a href="#h3-0-674" id="h3-0-674" class="i">+#endif`,QF=`LambertMaterial material;
   1811 </a><a href="#h3-0-675" id="h3-0-675" class="i">+material.diffuseColor = diffuseColor.rgb;
   1812 </a><a href="#h3-0-676" id="h3-0-676" class="i">+material.specularStrength = specularStrength;`,KF=`varying vec3 vViewPosition;
   1813 </a><a href="#h3-0-677" id="h3-0-677" class="i">+struct LambertMaterial {
   1814 </a><a href="#h3-0-678" id="h3-0-678" class="i">+	vec3 diffuseColor;
   1815 </a><a href="#h3-0-679" id="h3-0-679" class="i">+	float specularStrength;
   1816 </a><a href="#h3-0-680" id="h3-0-680" class="i">+};
   1817 </a><a href="#h3-0-681" id="h3-0-681" class="i">+void RE_Direct_Lambert( const in IncidentLight directLight, const in vec3 geometryPosition, const in vec3 geometryNormal, const in vec3 geometryViewDir, const in vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal, const in LambertMaterial material, inout ReflectedLight reflectedLight ) {
   1818 </a><a href="#h3-0-682" id="h3-0-682" class="i">+	float dotNL = saturate( dot( geometryNormal, directLight.direction ) );
   1819 </a><a href="#h3-0-683" id="h3-0-683" class="i">+	vec3 irradiance = dotNL * directLight.color;
   1820 </a><a href="#h3-0-684" id="h3-0-684" class="i">+	reflectedLight.directDiffuse += irradiance * BRDF_Lambert( material.diffuseColor );
   1821 </a><a href="#h3-0-685" id="h3-0-685" class="i">+}
   1822 </a><a href="#h3-0-686" id="h3-0-686" class="i">+void RE_IndirectDiffuse_Lambert( const in vec3 irradiance, const in vec3 geometryPosition, const in vec3 geometryNormal, const in vec3 geometryViewDir, const in vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal, const in LambertMaterial material, inout ReflectedLight reflectedLight ) {
   1823 </a><a href="#h3-0-687" id="h3-0-687" class="i">+	reflectedLight.indirectDiffuse += irradiance * BRDF_Lambert( material.diffuseColor );
   1824 </a><a href="#h3-0-688" id="h3-0-688" class="i">+}
   1825 </a><a href="#h3-0-689" id="h3-0-689" class="i">+#define RE_Direct				RE_Direct_Lambert
   1826 </a><a href="#h3-0-690" id="h3-0-690" class="i">+#define RE_IndirectDiffuse		RE_IndirectDiffuse_Lambert`,JF=`uniform bool receiveShadow;
   1827 </a><a href="#h3-0-691" id="h3-0-691" class="i">+uniform vec3 ambientLightColor;
   1828 </a><a href="#h3-0-692" id="h3-0-692" class="i">+#if defined( USE_LIGHT_PROBES )
   1829 </a><a href="#h3-0-693" id="h3-0-693" class="i">+	uniform vec3 lightProbe[ 9 ];
   1830 </a><a href="#h3-0-694" id="h3-0-694" class="i">+#endif
   1831 </a><a href="#h3-0-695" id="h3-0-695" class="i">+vec3 shGetIrradianceAt( in vec3 normal, in vec3 shCoefficients[ 9 ] ) {
   1832 </a><a href="#h3-0-696" id="h3-0-696" class="i">+	float x = normal.x, y = normal.y, z = normal.z;
   1833 </a><a href="#h3-0-697" id="h3-0-697" class="i">+	vec3 result = shCoefficients[ 0 ] * 0.886227;
   1834 </a><a href="#h3-0-698" id="h3-0-698" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 1 ] * 2.0 * 0.511664 * y;
   1835 </a><a href="#h3-0-699" id="h3-0-699" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 2 ] * 2.0 * 0.511664 * z;
   1836 </a><a href="#h3-0-700" id="h3-0-700" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 3 ] * 2.0 * 0.511664 * x;
   1837 </a><a href="#h3-0-701" id="h3-0-701" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 4 ] * 2.0 * 0.429043 * x * y;
   1838 </a><a href="#h3-0-702" id="h3-0-702" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 5 ] * 2.0 * 0.429043 * y * z;
   1839 </a><a href="#h3-0-703" id="h3-0-703" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 6 ] * ( 0.743125 * z * z - 0.247708 );
   1840 </a><a href="#h3-0-704" id="h3-0-704" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 7 ] * 2.0 * 0.429043 * x * z;
   1841 </a><a href="#h3-0-705" id="h3-0-705" class="i">+	result += shCoefficients[ 8 ] * 0.429043 * ( x * x - y * y );
   1842 </a><a href="#h3-0-706" id="h3-0-706" class="i">+	return result;
   1843 </a><a href="#h3-0-707" id="h3-0-707" class="i">+}
   1844 </a><a href="#h3-0-708" id="h3-0-708" class="i">+vec3 getLightProbeIrradiance( const in vec3 lightProbe[ 9 ], const in vec3 normal ) {
   1845 </a><a href="#h3-0-709" id="h3-0-709" class="i">+	vec3 worldNormal = inverseTransformDirection( normal, viewMatrix );
   1846 </a><a href="#h3-0-710" id="h3-0-710" class="i">+	vec3 irradiance = shGetIrradianceAt( worldNormal, lightProbe );
   1847 </a><a href="#h3-0-711" id="h3-0-711" class="i">+	return irradiance;
   1848 </a><a href="#h3-0-712" id="h3-0-712" class="i">+}
   1849 </a><a href="#h3-0-713" id="h3-0-713" class="i">+vec3 getAmbientLightIrradiance( const in vec3 ambientLightColor ) {
   1850 </a><a href="#h3-0-714" id="h3-0-714" class="i">+	vec3 irradiance = ambientLightColor;

   1852 </a><a href="#h3-0-716" id="h3-0-716" class="i">+}
   1853 </a><a href="#h3-0-717" id="h3-0-717" class="i">+float getDistanceAttenuation( const in float lightDistance, const in float cutoffDistance, const in float decayExponent ) {
   1854 </a><a href="#h3-0-718" id="h3-0-718" class="i">+	float distanceFalloff = 1.0 / max( pow( lightDistance, decayExponent ), 0.01 );
   1855 </a><a href="#h3-0-719" id="h3-0-719" class="i">+	if ( cutoffDistance &gt; 0.0 ) {
   1856 </a><a href="#h3-0-720" id="h3-0-720" class="i">+		distanceFalloff *= pow2( saturate( 1.0 - pow4( lightDistance / cutoffDistance ) ) );
   1857 </a><a href="#h3-0-721" id="h3-0-721" class="i">+	}
   1858 </a><a href="#h3-0-722" id="h3-0-722" class="i">+	return distanceFalloff;
   1859 </a><a href="#h3-0-723" id="h3-0-723" class="i">+}
   1860 </a><a href="#h3-0-724" id="h3-0-724" class="i">+float getSpotAttenuation( const in float coneCosine, const in float penumbraCosine, const in float angleCosine ) {
   1861 </a><a href="#h3-0-725" id="h3-0-725" class="i">+	return smoothstep( coneCosine, penumbraCosine, angleCosine );
   1862 </a><a href="#h3-0-726" id="h3-0-726" class="i">+}

   1903 </a><a href="#h3-0-767" id="h3-0-767" class="i">+	void getSpotLightInfo( const in SpotLight spotLight, const in vec3 geometryPosition, out IncidentLight light ) {

   1916 </a><a href="#h3-0-780" id="h3-0-780" class="i">+		}
   1917 </a><a href="#h3-0-781" id="h3-0-781" class="i">+	}

   1943 </a><a href="#h3-0-807" id="h3-0-807" class="i">+	vec3 getIBLIrradiance( const in vec3 normal ) {
   1944 </a><a href="#h3-0-808" id="h3-0-808" class="i">+		#ifdef ENVMAP_TYPE_CUBE_UV
   1945 </a><a href="#h3-0-809" id="h3-0-809" class="i">+			vec3 worldNormal = inverseTransformDirection( normal, viewMatrix );
   1946 </a><a href="#h3-0-810" id="h3-0-810" class="i">+			vec4 envMapColor = textureCubeUV( envMap, envMapRotation * worldNormal, 1.0 );
   1947 </a><a href="#h3-0-811" id="h3-0-811" class="i">+			return PI * envMapColor.rgb * envMapIntensity;
   1948 </a><a href="#h3-0-812" id="h3-0-812" class="i">+		#else

   1952 </a><a href="#h3-0-816" id="h3-0-816" class="i">+	vec3 getIBLRadiance( const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, const in float roughness ) {
   1953 </a><a href="#h3-0-817" id="h3-0-817" class="i">+		#ifdef ENVMAP_TYPE_CUBE_UV
   1954 </a><a href="#h3-0-818" id="h3-0-818" class="i">+			vec3 reflectVec = reflect( - viewDir, normal );
   1955 </a><a href="#h3-0-819" id="h3-0-819" class="i">+			reflectVec = normalize( mix( reflectVec, normal, roughness * roughness) );
   1956 </a><a href="#h3-0-820" id="h3-0-820" class="i">+			reflectVec = inverseTransformDirection( reflectVec, viewMatrix );
   1957 </a><a href="#h3-0-821" id="h3-0-821" class="i">+			vec4 envMapColor = textureCubeUV( envMap, envMapRotation * reflectVec, roughness );
   1958 </a><a href="#h3-0-822" id="h3-0-822" class="i">+			return envMapColor.rgb * envMapIntensity;
   1959 </a><a href="#h3-0-823" id="h3-0-823" class="i">+		#else
   1960 </a><a href="#h3-0-824" id="h3-0-824" class="i">+			return vec3( 0.0 );
   1961 </a><a href="#h3-0-825" id="h3-0-825" class="i">+		#endif
   1962 </a><a href="#h3-0-826" id="h3-0-826" class="i">+	}
   1963 </a><a href="#h3-0-827" id="h3-0-827" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_ANISOTROPY
   1964 </a><a href="#h3-0-828" id="h3-0-828" class="i">+		vec3 getIBLAnisotropyRadiance( const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, const in float roughness, const in vec3 bitangent, const in float anisotropy ) {
   1965 </a><a href="#h3-0-829" id="h3-0-829" class="i">+			#ifdef ENVMAP_TYPE_CUBE_UV
   1966 </a><a href="#h3-0-830" id="h3-0-830" class="i">+				vec3 bentNormal = cross( bitangent, viewDir );
   1967 </a><a href="#h3-0-831" id="h3-0-831" class="i">+				bentNormal = normalize( cross( bentNormal, bitangent ) );
   1968 </a><a href="#h3-0-832" id="h3-0-832" class="i">+				bentNormal = normalize( mix( bentNormal, normal, pow2( pow2( 1.0 - anisotropy * ( 1.0 - roughness ) ) ) ) );
   1969 </a><a href="#h3-0-833" id="h3-0-833" class="i">+				return getIBLRadiance( viewDir, bentNormal, roughness );

   1972 </a><a href="#h3-0-836" id="h3-0-836" class="i">+			#endif

   1974 </a><a href="#h3-0-838" id="h3-0-838" class="i">+	#endif

   2140 </a><a href="#h3-0-1004" id="h3-0-1004" class="i">+    float x = clamp( 1.0 - dotVH, 0.0, 1.0 );
   2141 </a><a href="#h3-0-1005" id="h3-0-1005" class="i">+    float x2 = x * x;
   2142 </a><a href="#h3-0-1006" id="h3-0-1006" class="i">+    float x5 = clamp( x * x2 * x2, 0.0, 0.9999 );
   2143 </a><a href="#h3-0-1007" id="h3-0-1007" class="i">+    return ( f - vec3( f90 ) * x5 ) / ( 1.0 - x5 );
   2144 </a><a href="#h3-0-1008" id="h3-0-1008" class="i">+}
   2145 </a><a href="#h3-0-1009" id="h3-0-1009" class="i">+float V_GGX_SmithCorrelated( const in float alpha, const in float dotNL, const in float dotNV ) {

   2147 </a><a href="#h3-0-1011" id="h3-0-1011" class="i">+	float gv = dotNL * sqrt( a2 + ( 1.0 - a2 ) * pow2( dotNV ) );
   2148 </a><a href="#h3-0-1012" id="h3-0-1012" class="i">+	float gl = dotNV * sqrt( a2 + ( 1.0 - a2 ) * pow2( dotNL ) );
   2149 </a><a href="#h3-0-1013" id="h3-0-1013" class="i">+	return 0.5 / max( gv + gl, EPSILON );
   2150 </a><a href="#h3-0-1014" id="h3-0-1014" class="i">+}
   2151 </a><a href="#h3-0-1015" id="h3-0-1015" class="i">+float D_GGX( const in float alpha, const in float dotNH ) {
   2152 </a><a href="#h3-0-1016" id="h3-0-1016" class="i">+	float a2 = pow2( alpha );
   2153 </a><a href="#h3-0-1017" id="h3-0-1017" class="i">+	float denom = pow2( dotNH ) * ( a2 - 1.0 ) + 1.0;
   2154 </a><a href="#h3-0-1018" id="h3-0-1018" class="i">+	return RECIPROCAL_PI * a2 / pow2( denom );
   2155 </a><a href="#h3-0-1019" id="h3-0-1019" class="i">+}
   2156 </a><a href="#h3-0-1020" id="h3-0-1020" class="i">+#ifdef USE_ANISOTROPY
   2157 </a><a href="#h3-0-1021" id="h3-0-1021" class="i">+	float V_GGX_SmithCorrelated_Anisotropic( const in float alphaT, const in float alphaB, const in float dotTV, const in float dotBV, const in float dotTL, const in float dotBL, const in float dotNV, const in float dotNL ) {
   2158 </a><a href="#h3-0-1022" id="h3-0-1022" class="i">+		float gv = dotNL * length( vec3( alphaT * dotTV, alphaB * dotBV, dotNV ) );
   2159 </a><a href="#h3-0-1023" id="h3-0-1023" class="i">+		float gl = dotNV * length( vec3( alphaT * dotTL, alphaB * dotBL, dotNL ) );
   2160 </a><a href="#h3-0-1024" id="h3-0-1024" class="i">+		float v = 0.5 / ( gv + gl );
   2161 </a><a href="#h3-0-1025" id="h3-0-1025" class="i">+		return saturate(v);
   2162 </a><a href="#h3-0-1026" id="h3-0-1026" class="i">+	}
   2163 </a><a href="#h3-0-1027" id="h3-0-1027" class="i">+	float D_GGX_Anisotropic( const in float alphaT, const in float alphaB, const in float dotNH, const in float dotTH, const in float dotBH ) {
   2164 </a><a href="#h3-0-1028" id="h3-0-1028" class="i">+		float a2 = alphaT * alphaB;
   2165 </a><a href="#h3-0-1029" id="h3-0-1029" class="i">+		highp vec3 v = vec3( alphaB * dotTH, alphaT * dotBH, a2 * dotNH );
   2166 </a><a href="#h3-0-1030" id="h3-0-1030" class="i">+		highp float v2 = dot( v, v );
   2167 </a><a href="#h3-0-1031" id="h3-0-1031" class="i">+		float w2 = a2 / v2;
   2168 </a><a href="#h3-0-1032" id="h3-0-1032" class="i">+		return RECIPROCAL_PI * a2 * pow2 ( w2 );
   2169 </a><a href="#h3-0-1033" id="h3-0-1033" class="i">+	}
   2170 </a><a href="#h3-0-1034" id="h3-0-1034" class="i">+#endif
   2171 </a><a href="#h3-0-1035" id="h3-0-1035" class="i">+#ifdef USE_CLEARCOAT
   2172 </a><a href="#h3-0-1036" id="h3-0-1036" class="i">+	vec3 BRDF_GGX_Clearcoat( const in vec3 lightDir, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, const in PhysicalMaterial material) {
   2173 </a><a href="#h3-0-1037" id="h3-0-1037" class="i">+		vec3 f0 = material.clearcoatF0;
   2174 </a><a href="#h3-0-1038" id="h3-0-1038" class="i">+		float f90 = material.clearcoatF90;
   2175 </a><a href="#h3-0-1039" id="h3-0-1039" class="i">+		float roughness = material.clearcoatRoughness;
   2176 </a><a href="#h3-0-1040" id="h3-0-1040" class="i">+		float alpha = pow2( roughness );
   2177 </a><a href="#h3-0-1041" id="h3-0-1041" class="i">+		vec3 halfDir = normalize( lightDir + viewDir );
   2178 </a><a href="#h3-0-1042" id="h3-0-1042" class="i">+		float dotNL = saturate( dot( normal, lightDir ) );
   2179 </a><a href="#h3-0-1043" id="h3-0-1043" class="i">+		float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   2180 </a><a href="#h3-0-1044" id="h3-0-1044" class="i">+		float dotNH = saturate( dot( normal, halfDir ) );
   2181 </a><a href="#h3-0-1045" id="h3-0-1045" class="i">+		float dotVH = saturate( dot( viewDir, halfDir ) );
   2182 </a><a href="#h3-0-1046" id="h3-0-1046" class="i">+		vec3 F = F_Schlick( f0, f90, dotVH );
   2183 </a><a href="#h3-0-1047" id="h3-0-1047" class="i">+		float V = V_GGX_SmithCorrelated( alpha, dotNL, dotNV );
   2184 </a><a href="#h3-0-1048" id="h3-0-1048" class="i">+		float D = D_GGX( alpha, dotNH );
   2185 </a><a href="#h3-0-1049" id="h3-0-1049" class="i">+		return F * ( V * D );
   2186 </a><a href="#h3-0-1050" id="h3-0-1050" class="i">+	}
   2187 </a><a href="#h3-0-1051" id="h3-0-1051" class="i">+#endif
   2188 </a><a href="#h3-0-1052" id="h3-0-1052" class="i">+vec3 BRDF_GGX( const in vec3 lightDir, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, const in PhysicalMaterial material ) {
   2189 </a><a href="#h3-0-1053" id="h3-0-1053" class="i">+	vec3 f0 = material.specularColor;
   2190 </a><a href="#h3-0-1054" id="h3-0-1054" class="i">+	float f90 = material.specularF90;
   2191 </a><a href="#h3-0-1055" id="h3-0-1055" class="i">+	float roughness = material.roughness;
   2192 </a><a href="#h3-0-1056" id="h3-0-1056" class="i">+	float alpha = pow2( roughness );
   2193 </a><a href="#h3-0-1057" id="h3-0-1057" class="i">+	vec3 halfDir = normalize( lightDir + viewDir );
   2194 </a><a href="#h3-0-1058" id="h3-0-1058" class="i">+	float dotNL = saturate( dot( normal, lightDir ) );
   2195 </a><a href="#h3-0-1059" id="h3-0-1059" class="i">+	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   2196 </a><a href="#h3-0-1060" id="h3-0-1060" class="i">+	float dotNH = saturate( dot( normal, halfDir ) );
   2197 </a><a href="#h3-0-1061" id="h3-0-1061" class="i">+	float dotVH = saturate( dot( viewDir, halfDir ) );
   2198 </a><a href="#h3-0-1062" id="h3-0-1062" class="i">+	vec3 F = F_Schlick( f0, f90, dotVH );
   2199 </a><a href="#h3-0-1063" id="h3-0-1063" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   2200 </a><a href="#h3-0-1064" id="h3-0-1064" class="i">+		F = mix( F, material.iridescenceFresnel, material.iridescence );
   2201 </a><a href="#h3-0-1065" id="h3-0-1065" class="i">+	#endif
   2202 </a><a href="#h3-0-1066" id="h3-0-1066" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_ANISOTROPY
   2203 </a><a href="#h3-0-1067" id="h3-0-1067" class="i">+		float dotTL = dot( material.anisotropyT, lightDir );
   2204 </a><a href="#h3-0-1068" id="h3-0-1068" class="i">+		float dotTV = dot( material.anisotropyT, viewDir );
   2205 </a><a href="#h3-0-1069" id="h3-0-1069" class="i">+		float dotTH = dot( material.anisotropyT, halfDir );
   2206 </a><a href="#h3-0-1070" id="h3-0-1070" class="i">+		float dotBL = dot( material.anisotropyB, lightDir );
   2207 </a><a href="#h3-0-1071" id="h3-0-1071" class="i">+		float dotBV = dot( material.anisotropyB, viewDir );
   2208 </a><a href="#h3-0-1072" id="h3-0-1072" class="i">+		float dotBH = dot( material.anisotropyB, halfDir );
   2209 </a><a href="#h3-0-1073" id="h3-0-1073" class="i">+		float V = V_GGX_SmithCorrelated_Anisotropic( material.alphaT, alpha, dotTV, dotBV, dotTL, dotBL, dotNV, dotNL );
   2210 </a><a href="#h3-0-1074" id="h3-0-1074" class="i">+		float D = D_GGX_Anisotropic( material.alphaT, alpha, dotNH, dotTH, dotBH );
   2211 </a><a href="#h3-0-1075" id="h3-0-1075" class="i">+	#else
   2212 </a><a href="#h3-0-1076" id="h3-0-1076" class="i">+		float V = V_GGX_SmithCorrelated( alpha, dotNL, dotNV );
   2213 </a><a href="#h3-0-1077" id="h3-0-1077" class="i">+		float D = D_GGX( alpha, dotNH );
   2214 </a><a href="#h3-0-1078" id="h3-0-1078" class="i">+	#endif
   2215 </a><a href="#h3-0-1079" id="h3-0-1079" class="i">+	return F * ( V * D );
   2216 </a><a href="#h3-0-1080" id="h3-0-1080" class="i">+}
   2217 </a><a href="#h3-0-1081" id="h3-0-1081" class="i">+vec2 LTC_Uv( const in vec3 N, const in vec3 V, const in float roughness ) {
   2218 </a><a href="#h3-0-1082" id="h3-0-1082" class="i">+	const float LUT_SIZE = 64.0;
   2219 </a><a href="#h3-0-1083" id="h3-0-1083" class="i">+	const float LUT_SCALE = ( LUT_SIZE - 1.0 ) / LUT_SIZE;
   2220 </a><a href="#h3-0-1084" id="h3-0-1084" class="i">+	const float LUT_BIAS = 0.5 / LUT_SIZE;
   2221 </a><a href="#h3-0-1085" id="h3-0-1085" class="i">+	float dotNV = saturate( dot( N, V ) );
   2222 </a><a href="#h3-0-1086" id="h3-0-1086" class="i">+	vec2 uv = vec2( roughness, sqrt( 1.0 - dotNV ) );
   2223 </a><a href="#h3-0-1087" id="h3-0-1087" class="i">+	uv = uv * LUT_SCALE + LUT_BIAS;
   2224 </a><a href="#h3-0-1088" id="h3-0-1088" class="i">+	return uv;
   2225 </a><a href="#h3-0-1089" id="h3-0-1089" class="i">+}
   2226 </a><a href="#h3-0-1090" id="h3-0-1090" class="i">+float LTC_ClippedSphereFormFactor( const in vec3 f ) {
   2227 </a><a href="#h3-0-1091" id="h3-0-1091" class="i">+	float l = length( f );
   2228 </a><a href="#h3-0-1092" id="h3-0-1092" class="i">+	return max( ( l * l + f.z ) / ( l + 1.0 ), 0.0 );
   2229 </a><a href="#h3-0-1093" id="h3-0-1093" class="i">+}
   2230 </a><a href="#h3-0-1094" id="h3-0-1094" class="i">+vec3 LTC_EdgeVectorFormFactor( const in vec3 v1, const in vec3 v2 ) {
   2231 </a><a href="#h3-0-1095" id="h3-0-1095" class="i">+	float x = dot( v1, v2 );
   2232 </a><a href="#h3-0-1096" id="h3-0-1096" class="i">+	float y = abs( x );
   2233 </a><a href="#h3-0-1097" id="h3-0-1097" class="i">+	float a = 0.8543985 + ( 0.4965155 + 0.0145206 * y ) * y;
   2234 </a><a href="#h3-0-1098" id="h3-0-1098" class="i">+	float b = 3.4175940 + ( 4.1616724 + y ) * y;
   2235 </a><a href="#h3-0-1099" id="h3-0-1099" class="i">+	float v = a / b;
   2236 </a><a href="#h3-0-1100" id="h3-0-1100" class="i">+	float theta_sintheta = ( x &gt; 0.0 ) ? v : 0.5 * inversesqrt( max( 1.0 - x * x, 1e-7 ) ) - v;
   2237 </a><a href="#h3-0-1101" id="h3-0-1101" class="i">+	return cross( v1, v2 ) * theta_sintheta;
   2238 </a><a href="#h3-0-1102" id="h3-0-1102" class="i">+}
   2239 </a><a href="#h3-0-1103" id="h3-0-1103" class="i">+vec3 LTC_Evaluate( const in vec3 N, const in vec3 V, const in vec3 P, const in mat3 mInv, const in vec3 rectCoords[ 4 ] ) {
   2240 </a><a href="#h3-0-1104" id="h3-0-1104" class="i">+	vec3 v1 = rectCoords[ 1 ] - rectCoords[ 0 ];
   2241 </a><a href="#h3-0-1105" id="h3-0-1105" class="i">+	vec3 v2 = rectCoords[ 3 ] - rectCoords[ 0 ];
   2242 </a><a href="#h3-0-1106" id="h3-0-1106" class="i">+	vec3 lightNormal = cross( v1, v2 );
   2243 </a><a href="#h3-0-1107" id="h3-0-1107" class="i">+	if( dot( lightNormal, P - rectCoords[ 0 ] ) &lt; 0.0 ) return vec3( 0.0 );
   2244 </a><a href="#h3-0-1108" id="h3-0-1108" class="i">+	vec3 T1, T2;
   2245 </a><a href="#h3-0-1109" id="h3-0-1109" class="i">+	T1 = normalize( V - N * dot( V, N ) );
   2246 </a><a href="#h3-0-1110" id="h3-0-1110" class="i">+	T2 = - cross( N, T1 );
   2247 </a><a href="#h3-0-1111" id="h3-0-1111" class="i">+	mat3 mat = mInv * transposeMat3( mat3( T1, T2, N ) );
   2248 </a><a href="#h3-0-1112" id="h3-0-1112" class="i">+	vec3 coords[ 4 ];
   2249 </a><a href="#h3-0-1113" id="h3-0-1113" class="i">+	coords[ 0 ] = mat * ( rectCoords[ 0 ] - P );
   2250 </a><a href="#h3-0-1114" id="h3-0-1114" class="i">+	coords[ 1 ] = mat * ( rectCoords[ 1 ] - P );
   2251 </a><a href="#h3-0-1115" id="h3-0-1115" class="i">+	coords[ 2 ] = mat * ( rectCoords[ 2 ] - P );
   2252 </a><a href="#h3-0-1116" id="h3-0-1116" class="i">+	coords[ 3 ] = mat * ( rectCoords[ 3 ] - P );
   2253 </a><a href="#h3-0-1117" id="h3-0-1117" class="i">+	coords[ 0 ] = normalize( coords[ 0 ] );
   2254 </a><a href="#h3-0-1118" id="h3-0-1118" class="i">+	coords[ 1 ] = normalize( coords[ 1 ] );
   2255 </a><a href="#h3-0-1119" id="h3-0-1119" class="i">+	coords[ 2 ] = normalize( coords[ 2 ] );
   2256 </a><a href="#h3-0-1120" id="h3-0-1120" class="i">+	coords[ 3 ] = normalize( coords[ 3 ] );
   2257 </a><a href="#h3-0-1121" id="h3-0-1121" class="i">+	vec3 vectorFormFactor = vec3( 0.0 );
   2258 </a><a href="#h3-0-1122" id="h3-0-1122" class="i">+	vectorFormFactor += LTC_EdgeVectorFormFactor( coords[ 0 ], coords[ 1 ] );
   2259 </a><a href="#h3-0-1123" id="h3-0-1123" class="i">+	vectorFormFactor += LTC_EdgeVectorFormFactor( coords[ 1 ], coords[ 2 ] );
   2260 </a><a href="#h3-0-1124" id="h3-0-1124" class="i">+	vectorFormFactor += LTC_EdgeVectorFormFactor( coords[ 2 ], coords[ 3 ] );
   2261 </a><a href="#h3-0-1125" id="h3-0-1125" class="i">+	vectorFormFactor += LTC_EdgeVectorFormFactor( coords[ 3 ], coords[ 0 ] );
   2262 </a><a href="#h3-0-1126" id="h3-0-1126" class="i">+	float result = LTC_ClippedSphereFormFactor( vectorFormFactor );
   2263 </a><a href="#h3-0-1127" id="h3-0-1127" class="i">+	return vec3( result );
   2264 </a><a href="#h3-0-1128" id="h3-0-1128" class="i">+}
   2265 </a><a href="#h3-0-1129" id="h3-0-1129" class="i">+#if defined( USE_SHEEN )
   2266 </a><a href="#h3-0-1130" id="h3-0-1130" class="i">+float D_Charlie( float roughness, float dotNH ) {
   2267 </a><a href="#h3-0-1131" id="h3-0-1131" class="i">+	float alpha = pow2( roughness );
   2268 </a><a href="#h3-0-1132" id="h3-0-1132" class="i">+	float invAlpha = 1.0 / alpha;
   2269 </a><a href="#h3-0-1133" id="h3-0-1133" class="i">+	float cos2h = dotNH * dotNH;
   2270 </a><a href="#h3-0-1134" id="h3-0-1134" class="i">+	float sin2h = max( 1.0 - cos2h, 0.0078125 );
   2271 </a><a href="#h3-0-1135" id="h3-0-1135" class="i">+	return ( 2.0 + invAlpha ) * pow( sin2h, invAlpha * 0.5 ) / ( 2.0 * PI );
   2272 </a><a href="#h3-0-1136" id="h3-0-1136" class="i">+}
   2273 </a><a href="#h3-0-1137" id="h3-0-1137" class="i">+float V_Neubelt( float dotNV, float dotNL ) {
   2274 </a><a href="#h3-0-1138" id="h3-0-1138" class="i">+	return saturate( 1.0 / ( 4.0 * ( dotNL + dotNV - dotNL * dotNV ) ) );
   2275 </a><a href="#h3-0-1139" id="h3-0-1139" class="i">+}
   2276 </a><a href="#h3-0-1140" id="h3-0-1140" class="i">+vec3 BRDF_Sheen( const in vec3 lightDir, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 normal, vec3 sheenColor, const in float sheenRoughness ) {
   2277 </a><a href="#h3-0-1141" id="h3-0-1141" class="i">+	vec3 halfDir = normalize( lightDir + viewDir );
   2278 </a><a href="#h3-0-1142" id="h3-0-1142" class="i">+	float dotNL = saturate( dot( normal, lightDir ) );
   2279 </a><a href="#h3-0-1143" id="h3-0-1143" class="i">+	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   2280 </a><a href="#h3-0-1144" id="h3-0-1144" class="i">+	float dotNH = saturate( dot( normal, halfDir ) );
   2281 </a><a href="#h3-0-1145" id="h3-0-1145" class="i">+	float D = D_Charlie( sheenRoughness, dotNH );
   2282 </a><a href="#h3-0-1146" id="h3-0-1146" class="i">+	float V = V_Neubelt( dotNV, dotNL );
   2283 </a><a href="#h3-0-1147" id="h3-0-1147" class="i">+	return sheenColor * ( D * V );
   2284 </a><a href="#h3-0-1148" id="h3-0-1148" class="i">+}
   2285 </a><a href="#h3-0-1149" id="h3-0-1149" class="i">+#endif
   2286 </a><a href="#h3-0-1150" id="h3-0-1150" class="i">+float IBLSheenBRDF( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in float roughness ) {
   2287 </a><a href="#h3-0-1151" id="h3-0-1151" class="i">+	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   2288 </a><a href="#h3-0-1152" id="h3-0-1152" class="i">+	float r2 = roughness * roughness;
   2289 </a><a href="#h3-0-1153" id="h3-0-1153" class="i">+	float a = roughness &lt; 0.25 ? -339.2 * r2 + 161.4 * roughness - 25.9 : -8.48 * r2 + 14.3 * roughness - 9.95;
   2290 </a><a href="#h3-0-1154" id="h3-0-1154" class="i">+	float b = roughness &lt; 0.25 ? 44.0 * r2 - 23.7 * roughness + 3.26 : 1.97 * r2 - 3.27 * roughness + 0.72;
   2291 </a><a href="#h3-0-1155" id="h3-0-1155" class="i">+	float DG = exp( a * dotNV + b ) + ( roughness &lt; 0.25 ? 0.0 : 0.1 * ( roughness - 0.25 ) );
   2292 </a><a href="#h3-0-1156" id="h3-0-1156" class="i">+	return saturate( DG * RECIPROCAL_PI );
   2293 </a><a href="#h3-0-1157" id="h3-0-1157" class="i">+}
   2294 </a><a href="#h3-0-1158" id="h3-0-1158" class="i">+vec2 DFGApprox( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in float roughness ) {
   2295 </a><a href="#h3-0-1159" id="h3-0-1159" class="i">+	float dotNV = saturate( dot( normal, viewDir ) );
   2296 </a><a href="#h3-0-1160" id="h3-0-1160" class="i">+	const vec4 c0 = vec4( - 1, - 0.0275, - 0.572, 0.022 );
   2297 </a><a href="#h3-0-1161" id="h3-0-1161" class="i">+	const vec4 c1 = vec4( 1, 0.0425, 1.04, - 0.04 );
   2298 </a><a href="#h3-0-1162" id="h3-0-1162" class="i">+	vec4 r = roughness * c0 + c1;
   2299 </a><a href="#h3-0-1163" id="h3-0-1163" class="i">+	float a004 = min( r.x * r.x, exp2( - 9.28 * dotNV ) ) * r.x + r.y;
   2300 </a><a href="#h3-0-1164" id="h3-0-1164" class="i">+	vec2 fab = vec2( - 1.04, 1.04 ) * a004 + r.zw;
   2301 </a><a href="#h3-0-1165" id="h3-0-1165" class="i">+	return fab;
   2302 </a><a href="#h3-0-1166" id="h3-0-1166" class="i">+}
   2303 </a><a href="#h3-0-1167" id="h3-0-1167" class="i">+vec3 EnvironmentBRDF( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in float roughness ) {
   2304 </a><a href="#h3-0-1168" id="h3-0-1168" class="i">+	vec2 fab = DFGApprox( normal, viewDir, roughness );
   2305 </a><a href="#h3-0-1169" id="h3-0-1169" class="i">+	return specularColor * fab.x + specularF90 * fab.y;
   2306 </a><a href="#h3-0-1170" id="h3-0-1170" class="i">+}
   2307 </a><a href="#h3-0-1171" id="h3-0-1171" class="i">+#ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   2308 </a><a href="#h3-0-1172" id="h3-0-1172" class="i">+void computeMultiscatteringIridescence( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in float iridescence, const in vec3 iridescenceF0, const in float roughness, inout vec3 singleScatter, inout vec3 multiScatter ) {
   2309 </a><a href="#h3-0-1173" id="h3-0-1173" class="i">+#else
   2310 </a><a href="#h3-0-1174" id="h3-0-1174" class="i">+void computeMultiscattering( const in vec3 normal, const in vec3 viewDir, const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in float roughness, inout vec3 singleScatter, inout vec3 multiScatter ) {
   2311 </a><a href="#h3-0-1175" id="h3-0-1175" class="i">+#endif
   2312 </a><a href="#h3-0-1176" id="h3-0-1176" class="i">+	vec2 fab = DFGApprox( normal, viewDir, roughness );
   2313 </a><a href="#h3-0-1177" id="h3-0-1177" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   2314 </a><a href="#h3-0-1178" id="h3-0-1178" class="i">+		vec3 Fr = mix( specularColor, iridescenceF0, iridescence );
   2315 </a><a href="#h3-0-1179" id="h3-0-1179" class="i">+	#else
   2316 </a><a href="#h3-0-1180" id="h3-0-1180" class="i">+		vec3 Fr = specularColor;
   2317 </a><a href="#h3-0-1181" id="h3-0-1181" class="i">+	#endif
   2318 </a><a href="#h3-0-1182" id="h3-0-1182" class="i">+	vec3 FssEss = Fr * fab.x + specularF90 * fab.y;
   2319 </a><a href="#h3-0-1183" id="h3-0-1183" class="i">+	float Ess = fab.x + fab.y;
   2320 </a><a href="#h3-0-1184" id="h3-0-1184" class="i">+	float Ems = 1.0 - Ess;
   2321 </a><a href="#h3-0-1185" id="h3-0-1185" class="i">+	vec3 Favg = Fr + ( 1.0 - Fr ) * 0.047619;	vec3 Fms = FssEss * Favg / ( 1.0 - Ems * Favg );
   2322 </a><a href="#h3-0-1186" id="h3-0-1186" class="i">+	singleScatter += FssEss;
   2323 </a><a href="#h3-0-1187" id="h3-0-1187" class="i">+	multiScatter += Fms * Ems;
   2324 </a><a href="#h3-0-1188" id="h3-0-1188" class="i">+}
   2325 </a><a href="#h3-0-1189" id="h3-0-1189" class="i">+#if NUM_RECT_AREA_LIGHTS &gt; 0
   2326 </a><a href="#h3-0-1190" id="h3-0-1190" class="i">+	void RE_Direct_RectArea_Physical( const in RectAreaLight rectAreaLight, const in vec3 geometryPosition, const in vec3 geometryNormal, const in vec3 geometryViewDir, const in vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal, const in PhysicalMaterial material, inout ReflectedLight reflectedLight ) {
   2327 </a><a href="#h3-0-1191" id="h3-0-1191" class="i">+		vec3 normal = geometryNormal;
   2328 </a><a href="#h3-0-1192" id="h3-0-1192" class="i">+		vec3 viewDir = geometryViewDir;
   2329 </a><a href="#h3-0-1193" id="h3-0-1193" class="i">+		vec3 position = geometryPosition;
   2330 </a><a href="#h3-0-1194" id="h3-0-1194" class="i">+		vec3 lightPos = rectAreaLight.position;
   2331 </a><a href="#h3-0-1195" id="h3-0-1195" class="i">+		vec3 halfWidth = rectAreaLight.halfWidth;
   2332 </a><a href="#h3-0-1196" id="h3-0-1196" class="i">+		vec3 halfHeight = rectAreaLight.halfHeight;
   2333 </a><a href="#h3-0-1197" id="h3-0-1197" class="i">+		vec3 lightColor = rectAreaLight.color;
   2334 </a><a href="#h3-0-1198" id="h3-0-1198" class="i">+		float roughness = material.roughness;
   2335 </a><a href="#h3-0-1199" id="h3-0-1199" class="i">+		vec3 rectCoords[ 4 ];
   2336 </a><a href="#h3-0-1200" id="h3-0-1200" class="i">+		rectCoords[ 0 ] = lightPos + halfWidth - halfHeight;		rectCoords[ 1 ] = lightPos - halfWidth - halfHeight;
   2337 </a><a href="#h3-0-1201" id="h3-0-1201" class="i">+		rectCoords[ 2 ] = lightPos - halfWidth + halfHeight;
   2338 </a><a href="#h3-0-1202" id="h3-0-1202" class="i">+		rectCoords[ 3 ] = lightPos + halfWidth + halfHeight;
   2339 </a><a href="#h3-0-1203" id="h3-0-1203" class="i">+		vec2 uv = LTC_Uv( normal, viewDir, roughness );
   2340 </a><a href="#h3-0-1204" id="h3-0-1204" class="i">+		vec4 t1 = texture2D( ltc_1, uv );
   2341 </a><a href="#h3-0-1205" id="h3-0-1205" class="i">+		vec4 t2 = texture2D( ltc_2, uv );
   2342 </a><a href="#h3-0-1206" id="h3-0-1206" class="i">+		mat3 mInv = mat3(
   2343 </a><a href="#h3-0-1207" id="h3-0-1207" class="i">+			vec3( t1.x, 0, t1.y ),
   2344 </a><a href="#h3-0-1208" id="h3-0-1208" class="i">+			vec3(    0, 1,    0 ),
   2345 </a><a href="#h3-0-1209" id="h3-0-1209" class="i">+			vec3( t1.z, 0, t1.w )
   2346 </a><a href="#h3-0-1210" id="h3-0-1210" class="i">+		);
   2347 </a><a href="#h3-0-1211" id="h3-0-1211" class="i">+		vec3 fresnel = ( material.specularColor * t2.x + ( vec3( 1.0 ) - material.specularColor ) * t2.y );
   2348 </a><a href="#h3-0-1212" id="h3-0-1212" class="i">+		reflectedLight.directSpecular += lightColor * fresnel * LTC_Evaluate( normal, viewDir, position, mInv, rectCoords );
   2349 </a><a href="#h3-0-1213" id="h3-0-1213" class="i">+		reflectedLight.directDiffuse += lightColor * material.diffuseColor * LTC_Evaluate( normal, viewDir, position, mat3( 1.0 ), rectCoords );
   2350 </a><a href="#h3-0-1214" id="h3-0-1214" class="i">+	}
   2351 </a><a href="#h3-0-1215" id="h3-0-1215" class="i">+#endif
   2352 </a><a href="#h3-0-1216" id="h3-0-1216" class="i">+void RE_Direct_Physical( const in IncidentLight directLight, const in vec3 geometryPosition, const in vec3 geometryNormal, const in vec3 geometryViewDir, const in vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal, const in PhysicalMaterial material, inout ReflectedLight reflectedLight ) {
   2353 </a><a href="#h3-0-1217" id="h3-0-1217" class="i">+	float dotNL = saturate( dot( geometryNormal, directLight.direction ) );
   2354 </a><a href="#h3-0-1218" id="h3-0-1218" class="i">+	vec3 irradiance = dotNL * directLight.color;
   2355 </a><a href="#h3-0-1219" id="h3-0-1219" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_CLEARCOAT
   2356 </a><a href="#h3-0-1220" id="h3-0-1220" class="i">+		float dotNLcc = saturate( dot( geometryClearcoatNormal, directLight.direction ) );
   2357 </a><a href="#h3-0-1221" id="h3-0-1221" class="i">+		vec3 ccIrradiance = dotNLcc * directLight.color;
   2358 </a><a href="#h3-0-1222" id="h3-0-1222" class="i">+		clearcoatSpecularDirect += ccIrradiance * BRDF_GGX_Clearcoat( directLight.direction, geometryViewDir, geometryClearcoatNormal, material );
   2359 </a><a href="#h3-0-1223" id="h3-0-1223" class="i">+	#endif
   2360 </a><a href="#h3-0-1224" id="h3-0-1224" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_SHEEN
   2361 </a><a href="#h3-0-1225" id="h3-0-1225" class="i">+		sheenSpecularDirect += irradiance * BRDF_Sheen( directLight.direction, geometryViewDir, geometryNormal, material.sheenColor, material.sheenRoughness );
   2362 </a><a href="#h3-0-1226" id="h3-0-1226" class="i">+	#endif
   2363 </a><a href="#h3-0-1227" id="h3-0-1227" class="i">+	reflectedLight.directSpecular += irradiance * BRDF_GGX( directLight.direction, geometryViewDir, geometryNormal, material );
   2364 </a><a href="#h3-0-1228" id="h3-0-1228" class="i">+	reflectedLight.directDiffuse += irradiance * BRDF_Lambert( material.diffuseColor );
   2365 </a><a href="#h3-0-1229" id="h3-0-1229" class="i">+}
   2366 </a><a href="#h3-0-1230" id="h3-0-1230" class="i">+void RE_IndirectDiffuse_Physical( const in vec3 irradiance, const in vec3 geometryPosition, const in vec3 geometryNormal, const in vec3 geometryViewDir, const in vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal, const in PhysicalMaterial material, inout ReflectedLight reflectedLight ) {
   2367 </a><a href="#h3-0-1231" id="h3-0-1231" class="i">+	reflectedLight.indirectDiffuse += irradiance * BRDF_Lambert( material.diffuseColor );
   2368 </a><a href="#h3-0-1232" id="h3-0-1232" class="i">+}
   2369 </a><a href="#h3-0-1233" id="h3-0-1233" class="i">+void RE_IndirectSpecular_Physical( const in vec3 radiance, const in vec3 irradiance, const in vec3 clearcoatRadiance, const in vec3 geometryPosition, const in vec3 geometryNormal, const in vec3 geometryViewDir, const in vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal, const in PhysicalMaterial material, inout ReflectedLight reflectedLight) {
   2370 </a><a href="#h3-0-1234" id="h3-0-1234" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_CLEARCOAT
   2371 </a><a href="#h3-0-1235" id="h3-0-1235" class="i">+		clearcoatSpecularIndirect += clearcoatRadiance * EnvironmentBRDF( geometryClearcoatNormal, geometryViewDir, material.clearcoatF0, material.clearcoatF90, material.clearcoatRoughness );
   2372 </a><a href="#h3-0-1236" id="h3-0-1236" class="i">+	#endif
   2373 </a><a href="#h3-0-1237" id="h3-0-1237" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_SHEEN
   2374 </a><a href="#h3-0-1238" id="h3-0-1238" class="i">+		sheenSpecularIndirect += irradiance * material.sheenColor * IBLSheenBRDF( geometryNormal, geometryViewDir, material.sheenRoughness );
   2375 </a><a href="#h3-0-1239" id="h3-0-1239" class="i">+	#endif
   2376 </a><a href="#h3-0-1240" id="h3-0-1240" class="i">+	vec3 singleScattering = vec3( 0.0 );
   2377 </a><a href="#h3-0-1241" id="h3-0-1241" class="i">+	vec3 multiScattering = vec3( 0.0 );
   2378 </a><a href="#h3-0-1242" id="h3-0-1242" class="i">+	vec3 cosineWeightedIrradiance = irradiance * RECIPROCAL_PI;
   2379 </a><a href="#h3-0-1243" id="h3-0-1243" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   2380 </a><a href="#h3-0-1244" id="h3-0-1244" class="i">+		computeMultiscatteringIridescence( geometryNormal, geometryViewDir, material.specularColor, material.specularF90, material.iridescence, material.iridescenceFresnel, material.roughness, singleScattering, multiScattering );
   2381 </a><a href="#h3-0-1245" id="h3-0-1245" class="i">+	#else
   2382 </a><a href="#h3-0-1246" id="h3-0-1246" class="i">+		computeMultiscattering( geometryNormal, geometryViewDir, material.specularColor, material.specularF90, material.roughness, singleScattering, multiScattering );
   2383 </a><a href="#h3-0-1247" id="h3-0-1247" class="i">+	#endif
   2384 </a><a href="#h3-0-1248" id="h3-0-1248" class="i">+	vec3 totalScattering = singleScattering + multiScattering;
   2385 </a><a href="#h3-0-1249" id="h3-0-1249" class="i">+	vec3 diffuse = material.diffuseColor * ( 1.0 - max( max( totalScattering.r, totalScattering.g ), totalScattering.b ) );
   2386 </a><a href="#h3-0-1250" id="h3-0-1250" class="i">+	reflectedLight.indirectSpecular += radiance * singleScattering;
   2387 </a><a href="#h3-0-1251" id="h3-0-1251" class="i">+	reflectedLight.indirectSpecular += multiScattering * cosineWeightedIrradiance;
   2388 </a><a href="#h3-0-1252" id="h3-0-1252" class="i">+	reflectedLight.indirectDiffuse += diffuse * cosineWeightedIrradiance;
   2389 </a><a href="#h3-0-1253" id="h3-0-1253" class="i">+}
   2390 </a><a href="#h3-0-1254" id="h3-0-1254" class="i">+#define RE_Direct				RE_Direct_Physical
   2391 </a><a href="#h3-0-1255" id="h3-0-1255" class="i">+#define RE_Direct_RectArea		RE_Direct_RectArea_Physical
   2392 </a><a href="#h3-0-1256" id="h3-0-1256" class="i">+#define RE_IndirectDiffuse		RE_IndirectDiffuse_Physical
   2393 </a><a href="#h3-0-1257" id="h3-0-1257" class="i">+#define RE_IndirectSpecular		RE_IndirectSpecular_Physical
   2394 </a><a href="#h3-0-1258" id="h3-0-1258" class="i">+float computeSpecularOcclusion( const in float dotNV, const in float ambientOcclusion, const in float roughness ) {
   2395 </a><a href="#h3-0-1259" id="h3-0-1259" class="i">+	return saturate( pow( dotNV + ambientOcclusion, exp2( - 16.0 * roughness - 1.0 ) ) - 1.0 + ambientOcclusion );
   2396 </a><a href="#h3-0-1260" id="h3-0-1260" class="i">+}`,rV=`
   2397 </a><a href="#h3-0-1261" id="h3-0-1261" class="i">+vec3 geometryPosition = - vViewPosition;
   2398 </a><a href="#h3-0-1262" id="h3-0-1262" class="i">+vec3 geometryNormal = normal;
   2399 </a><a href="#h3-0-1263" id="h3-0-1263" class="i">+vec3 geometryViewDir = ( isOrthographic ) ? vec3( 0, 0, 1 ) : normalize( vViewPosition );
   2400 </a><a href="#h3-0-1264" id="h3-0-1264" class="i">+vec3 geometryClearcoatNormal = vec3( 0.0 );
   2401 </a><a href="#h3-0-1265" id="h3-0-1265" class="i">+#ifdef USE_CLEARCOAT
   2402 </a><a href="#h3-0-1266" id="h3-0-1266" class="i">+	geometryClearcoatNormal = clearcoatNormal;
   2403 </a><a href="#h3-0-1267" id="h3-0-1267" class="i">+#endif
   2404 </a><a href="#h3-0-1268" id="h3-0-1268" class="i">+#ifdef USE_IRIDESCENCE
   2405 </a><a href="#h3-0-1269" id="h3-0-1269" class="i">+	float dotNVi = saturate( dot( normal, geometryViewDir ) );
   2406 </a><a href="#h3-0-1270" id="h3-0-1270" class="i">+	if ( material.iridescenceThickness == 0.0 ) {
   2407 </a><a href="#h3-0-1271" id="h3-0-1271" class="i">+		material.iridescence = 0.0;
   2408 </a><a href="#h3-0-1272" id="h3-0-1272" class="i">+	} else {
   2409 </a><a href="#h3-0-1273" id="h3-0-1273" class="i">+		material.iridescence = saturate( material.iridescence );
   2410 </a><a href="#h3-0-1274" id="h3-0-1274" class="i">+	}
   2411 </a><a href="#h3-0-1275" id="h3-0-1275" class="i">+	if ( material.iridescence &gt; 0.0 ) {
   2412 </a><a href="#h3-0-1276" id="h3-0-1276" class="i">+		material.iridescenceFresnel = evalIridescence( 1.0, material.iridescenceIOR, dotNVi, material.iridescenceThickness, material.specularColor );
   2413 </a><a href="#h3-0-1277" id="h3-0-1277" class="i">+		material.iridescenceF0 = Schlick_to_F0( material.iridescenceFresnel, 1.0, dotNVi );
   2414 </a><a href="#h3-0-1278" id="h3-0-1278" class="i">+	}
   2415 </a><a href="#h3-0-1279" id="h3-0-1279" class="i">+#endif
   2416 </a><a href="#h3-0-1280" id="h3-0-1280" class="i">+IncidentLight directLight;
   2417 </a><a href="#h3-0-1281" id="h3-0-1281" class="i">+#if ( NUM_POINT_LIGHTS &gt; 0 ) &amp;&amp; defined( RE_Direct )

   2419 </a><a href="#h3-0-1283" id="h3-0-1283" class="i">+	#if defined( USE_SHADOWMAP ) &amp;&amp; NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0

   2421 </a><a href="#h3-0-1285" id="h3-0-1285" class="i">+	#endif
   2422 </a><a href="#h3-0-1286" id="h3-0-1286" class="i">+	#pragma unroll_loop_start
   2423 </a><a href="#h3-0-1287" id="h3-0-1287" class="i">+	for ( int i = 0; i &lt; NUM_POINT_LIGHTS; i ++ ) {

   2425 </a><a href="#h3-0-1289" id="h3-0-1289" class="i">+		getPointLightInfo( pointLight, geometryPosition, directLight );
   2426 </a><a href="#h3-0-1290" id="h3-0-1290" class="i">+		#if defined( USE_SHADOWMAP ) &amp;&amp; ( UNROLLED_LOOP_INDEX &lt; NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS )

   2428 </a><a href="#h3-0-1292" id="h3-0-1292" class="i">+		directLight.color *= ( directLight.visible &amp;&amp; receiveShadow ) ? getPointShadow( pointShadowMap[ i ], pointLightShadow.shadowMapSize, pointLightShadow.shadowIntensity, pointLightShadow.shadowBias, pointLightShadow.shadowRadius, vPointShadowCoord[ i ], pointLightShadow.shadowCameraNear, pointLightShadow.shadowCameraFar ) : 1.0;
   2429 </a><a href="#h3-0-1293" id="h3-0-1293" class="i">+		#endif

   2431 </a><a href="#h3-0-1295" id="h3-0-1295" class="i">+	}

   2433 </a><a href="#h3-0-1297" id="h3-0-1297" class="i">+#endif
   2434 </a><a href="#h3-0-1298" id="h3-0-1298" class="i">+#if ( NUM_SPOT_LIGHTS &gt; 0 ) &amp;&amp; defined( RE_Direct )

   2455 </a><a href="#h3-0-1319" id="h3-0-1319" class="i">+			inSpotLightMap = all( lessThan( abs( spotLightCoord * 2. - 1. ), vec3( 1.0 ) ) );

   2796 </a><a href="#h3-0-1660" id="h3-0-1660" class="i">+}
   2797 </a><a href="#h3-0-1661" id="h3-0-1661" class="i">+vec4 pack2HalfToRGBA( const in vec2 v ) {
   2798 </a><a href="#h3-0-1662" id="h3-0-1662" class="i">+	vec4 r = vec4( v.x, fract( v.x * 255.0 ), v.y, fract( v.y * 255.0 ) );

   2801 </a><a href="#h3-0-1665" id="h3-0-1665" class="i">+vec2 unpackRGBATo2Half( const in vec4 v ) {
   2802 </a><a href="#h3-0-1666" id="h3-0-1666" class="i">+	return vec2( v.x + ( v.y / 255.0 ), v.z + ( v.w / 255.0 ) );
   2803 </a><a href="#h3-0-1667" id="h3-0-1667" class="i">+}
   2804 </a><a href="#h3-0-1668" id="h3-0-1668" class="i">+float viewZToOrthographicDepth( const in float viewZ, const in float near, const in float far ) {
   2805 </a><a href="#h3-0-1669" id="h3-0-1669" class="i">+	return ( viewZ + near ) / ( near - far );

   2811 </a><a href="#h3-0-1675" id="h3-0-1675" class="i">+	return ( ( near + viewZ ) * far ) / ( ( far - near ) * viewZ );

   2813 </a><a href="#h3-0-1677" id="h3-0-1677" class="i">+float perspectiveDepthToViewZ( const in float depth, const in float near, const in float far ) {

   2815 </a><a href="#h3-0-1679" id="h3-0-1679" class="i">+}`,BV=`#ifdef PREMULTIPLIED_ALPHA
   2816 </a><a href="#h3-0-1680" id="h3-0-1680" class="i">+	gl_FragColor.rgb *= gl_FragColor.a;
   2817 </a><a href="#h3-0-1681" id="h3-0-1681" class="i">+#endif`,PV=`vec4 mvPosition = vec4( transformed, 1.0 );
   2818 </a><a href="#h3-0-1682" id="h3-0-1682" class="i">+#ifdef USE_BATCHING

   2825 </a><a href="#h3-0-1689" id="h3-0-1689" class="i">+gl_Position = projectionMatrix * mvPosition;`,IV=`#ifdef DITHERING

   2827 </a><a href="#h3-0-1691" id="h3-0-1691" class="i">+#endif`,HV=`#ifdef DITHERING
   2828 </a><a href="#h3-0-1692" id="h3-0-1692" class="i">+	vec3 dithering( vec3 color ) {

   2837 </a><a href="#h3-0-1701" id="h3-0-1701" class="i">+	roughnessFactor *= texelRoughness.g;

   2884 </a><a href="#h3-0-1748" id="h3-0-1748" class="i">+	float texture2DCompare( sampler2D depths, vec2 uv, float compare ) {
   2885 </a><a href="#h3-0-1749" id="h3-0-1749" class="i">+		float depth = unpackRGBAToDepth( texture2D( depths, uv ) );
   2886 </a><a href="#h3-0-1750" id="h3-0-1750" class="i">+		#ifdef USE_REVERSEDEPTHBUF
