   2888 </a><a href="#h3-0-1752" id="h3-0-1752" class="i">+		#else
   2889 </a><a href="#h3-0-1753" id="h3-0-1753" class="i">+			return step( compare, depth );
   2890 </a><a href="#h3-0-1754" id="h3-0-1754" class="i">+		#endif
   2891 </a><a href="#h3-0-1755" id="h3-0-1755" class="i">+	}
   2892 </a><a href="#h3-0-1756" id="h3-0-1756" class="i">+	vec2 texture2DDistribution( sampler2D shadow, vec2 uv ) {
   2893 </a><a href="#h3-0-1757" id="h3-0-1757" class="i">+		return unpackRGBATo2Half( texture2D( shadow, uv ) );
   2894 </a><a href="#h3-0-1758" id="h3-0-1758" class="i">+	}
   2895 </a><a href="#h3-0-1759" id="h3-0-1759" class="i">+	float VSMShadow (sampler2D shadow, vec2 uv, float compare ){
   2896 </a><a href="#h3-0-1760" id="h3-0-1760" class="i">+		float occlusion = 1.0;
   2897 </a><a href="#h3-0-1761" id="h3-0-1761" class="i">+		vec2 distribution = texture2DDistribution( shadow, uv );
   2898 </a><a href="#h3-0-1762" id="h3-0-1762" class="i">+		#ifdef USE_REVERSEDEPTHBUF
   2899 </a><a href="#h3-0-1763" id="h3-0-1763" class="i">+			float hard_shadow = step( distribution.x, compare );
   2900 </a><a href="#h3-0-1764" id="h3-0-1764" class="i">+		#else
   2901 </a><a href="#h3-0-1765" id="h3-0-1765" class="i">+			float hard_shadow = step( compare , distribution.x );
   2902 </a><a href="#h3-0-1766" id="h3-0-1766" class="i">+		#endif
   2903 </a><a href="#h3-0-1767" id="h3-0-1767" class="i">+		if (hard_shadow != 1.0 ) {
   2904 </a><a href="#h3-0-1768" id="h3-0-1768" class="i">+			float distance = compare - distribution.x ;
   2905 </a><a href="#h3-0-1769" id="h3-0-1769" class="i">+			float variance = max( 0.00000, distribution.y * distribution.y );
   2906 </a><a href="#h3-0-1770" id="h3-0-1770" class="i">+			float softness_probability = variance / (variance + distance * distance );			softness_probability = clamp( ( softness_probability - 0.3 ) / ( 0.95 - 0.3 ), 0.0, 1.0 );			occlusion = clamp( max( hard_shadow, softness_probability ), 0.0, 1.0 );
   2907 </a><a href="#h3-0-1771" id="h3-0-1771" class="i">+		}
   2908 </a><a href="#h3-0-1772" id="h3-0-1772" class="i">+		return occlusion;
   2909 </a><a href="#h3-0-1773" id="h3-0-1773" class="i">+	}
   2910 </a><a href="#h3-0-1774" id="h3-0-1774" class="i">+	float getShadow( sampler2D shadowMap, vec2 shadowMapSize, float shadowIntensity, float shadowBias, float shadowRadius, vec4 shadowCoord ) {
   2911 </a><a href="#h3-0-1775" id="h3-0-1775" class="i">+		float shadow = 1.0;
   2912 </a><a href="#h3-0-1776" id="h3-0-1776" class="i">+		shadowCoord.xyz /= shadowCoord.w;
   2913 </a><a href="#h3-0-1777" id="h3-0-1777" class="i">+		shadowCoord.z += shadowBias;
   2914 </a><a href="#h3-0-1778" id="h3-0-1778" class="i">+		bool inFrustum = shadowCoord.x &gt;= 0.0 &amp;&amp; shadowCoord.x &lt;= 1.0 &amp;&amp; shadowCoord.y &gt;= 0.0 &amp;&amp; shadowCoord.y &lt;= 1.0;
   2915 </a><a href="#h3-0-1779" id="h3-0-1779" class="i">+		bool frustumTest = inFrustum &amp;&amp; shadowCoord.z &lt;= 1.0;
   2916 </a><a href="#h3-0-1780" id="h3-0-1780" class="i">+		if ( frustumTest ) {
   2917 </a><a href="#h3-0-1781" id="h3-0-1781" class="i">+		#if defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_PCF )
   2918 </a><a href="#h3-0-1782" id="h3-0-1782" class="i">+			vec2 texelSize = vec2( 1.0 ) / shadowMapSize;
   2919 </a><a href="#h3-0-1783" id="h3-0-1783" class="i">+			float dx0 = - texelSize.x * shadowRadius;
   2920 </a><a href="#h3-0-1784" id="h3-0-1784" class="i">+			float dy0 = - texelSize.y * shadowRadius;
   2921 </a><a href="#h3-0-1785" id="h3-0-1785" class="i">+			float dx1 = + texelSize.x * shadowRadius;
   2922 </a><a href="#h3-0-1786" id="h3-0-1786" class="i">+			float dy1 = + texelSize.y * shadowRadius;
   2923 </a><a href="#h3-0-1787" id="h3-0-1787" class="i">+			float dx2 = dx0 / 2.0;
   2924 </a><a href="#h3-0-1788" id="h3-0-1788" class="i">+			float dy2 = dy0 / 2.0;
   2925 </a><a href="#h3-0-1789" id="h3-0-1789" class="i">+			float dx3 = dx1 / 2.0;
   2926 </a><a href="#h3-0-1790" id="h3-0-1790" class="i">+			float dy3 = dy1 / 2.0;
   2927 </a><a href="#h3-0-1791" id="h3-0-1791" class="i">+			shadow = (
   2928 </a><a href="#h3-0-1792" id="h3-0-1792" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx0, dy0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2929 </a><a href="#h3-0-1793" id="h3-0-1793" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( 0.0, dy0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2930 </a><a href="#h3-0-1794" id="h3-0-1794" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx1, dy0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2931 </a><a href="#h3-0-1795" id="h3-0-1795" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx2, dy2 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2932 </a><a href="#h3-0-1796" id="h3-0-1796" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( 0.0, dy2 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2933 </a><a href="#h3-0-1797" id="h3-0-1797" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx3, dy2 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2934 </a><a href="#h3-0-1798" id="h3-0-1798" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx0, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2935 </a><a href="#h3-0-1799" id="h3-0-1799" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx2, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2936 </a><a href="#h3-0-1800" id="h3-0-1800" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy, shadowCoord.z ) +
   2937 </a><a href="#h3-0-1801" id="h3-0-1801" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx3, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2938 </a><a href="#h3-0-1802" id="h3-0-1802" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx1, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2939 </a><a href="#h3-0-1803" id="h3-0-1803" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx2, dy3 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2940 </a><a href="#h3-0-1804" id="h3-0-1804" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( 0.0, dy3 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2941 </a><a href="#h3-0-1805" id="h3-0-1805" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx3, dy3 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2942 </a><a href="#h3-0-1806" id="h3-0-1806" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx0, dy1 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2943 </a><a href="#h3-0-1807" id="h3-0-1807" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( 0.0, dy1 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2944 </a><a href="#h3-0-1808" id="h3-0-1808" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy + vec2( dx1, dy1 ), shadowCoord.z )
   2945 </a><a href="#h3-0-1809" id="h3-0-1809" class="i">+			) * ( 1.0 / 17.0 );
   2946 </a><a href="#h3-0-1810" id="h3-0-1810" class="i">+		#elif defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_PCF_SOFT )
   2947 </a><a href="#h3-0-1811" id="h3-0-1811" class="i">+			vec2 texelSize = vec2( 1.0 ) / shadowMapSize;
   2948 </a><a href="#h3-0-1812" id="h3-0-1812" class="i">+			float dx = texelSize.x;
   2949 </a><a href="#h3-0-1813" id="h3-0-1813" class="i">+			float dy = texelSize.y;
   2950 </a><a href="#h3-0-1814" id="h3-0-1814" class="i">+			vec2 uv = shadowCoord.xy;
   2951 </a><a href="#h3-0-1815" id="h3-0-1815" class="i">+			vec2 f = fract( uv * shadowMapSize + 0.5 );
   2952 </a><a href="#h3-0-1816" id="h3-0-1816" class="i">+			uv -= f * texelSize;
   2953 </a><a href="#h3-0-1817" id="h3-0-1817" class="i">+			shadow = (
   2954 </a><a href="#h3-0-1818" id="h3-0-1818" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv, shadowCoord.z ) +
   2955 </a><a href="#h3-0-1819" id="h3-0-1819" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( dx, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2956 </a><a href="#h3-0-1820" id="h3-0-1820" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 0.0, dy ), shadowCoord.z ) +
   2957 </a><a href="#h3-0-1821" id="h3-0-1821" class="i">+				texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + texelSize, shadowCoord.z ) +
   2958 </a><a href="#h3-0-1822" id="h3-0-1822" class="i">+				mix( texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( -dx, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2959 </a><a href="#h3-0-1823" id="h3-0-1823" class="i">+					 texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 2.0 * dx, 0.0 ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2960 </a><a href="#h3-0-1824" id="h3-0-1824" class="i">+					 f.x ) +
   2961 </a><a href="#h3-0-1825" id="h3-0-1825" class="i">+				mix( texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( -dx, dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2962 </a><a href="#h3-0-1826" id="h3-0-1826" class="i">+					 texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 2.0 * dx, dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2963 </a><a href="#h3-0-1827" id="h3-0-1827" class="i">+					 f.x ) +
   2964 </a><a href="#h3-0-1828" id="h3-0-1828" class="i">+				mix( texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 0.0, -dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2965 </a><a href="#h3-0-1829" id="h3-0-1829" class="i">+					 texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 0.0, 2.0 * dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2966 </a><a href="#h3-0-1830" id="h3-0-1830" class="i">+					 f.y ) +
   2967 </a><a href="#h3-0-1831" id="h3-0-1831" class="i">+				mix( texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( dx, -dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2968 </a><a href="#h3-0-1832" id="h3-0-1832" class="i">+					 texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( dx, 2.0 * dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2969 </a><a href="#h3-0-1833" id="h3-0-1833" class="i">+					 f.y ) +
   2970 </a><a href="#h3-0-1834" id="h3-0-1834" class="i">+				mix( mix( texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( -dx, -dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2971 </a><a href="#h3-0-1835" id="h3-0-1835" class="i">+						  texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 2.0 * dx, -dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2972 </a><a href="#h3-0-1836" id="h3-0-1836" class="i">+						  f.x ),
   2973 </a><a href="#h3-0-1837" id="h3-0-1837" class="i">+					 mix( texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( -dx, 2.0 * dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2974 </a><a href="#h3-0-1838" id="h3-0-1838" class="i">+						  texture2DCompare( shadowMap, uv + vec2( 2.0 * dx, 2.0 * dy ), shadowCoord.z ),
   2975 </a><a href="#h3-0-1839" id="h3-0-1839" class="i">+						  f.x ),
   2976 </a><a href="#h3-0-1840" id="h3-0-1840" class="i">+					 f.y )
   2977 </a><a href="#h3-0-1841" id="h3-0-1841" class="i">+			) * ( 1.0 / 9.0 );
   2978 </a><a href="#h3-0-1842" id="h3-0-1842" class="i">+		#elif defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_VSM )
   2979 </a><a href="#h3-0-1843" id="h3-0-1843" class="i">+			shadow = VSMShadow( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy, shadowCoord.z );
   2980 </a><a href="#h3-0-1844" id="h3-0-1844" class="i">+		#else
   2981 </a><a href="#h3-0-1845" id="h3-0-1845" class="i">+			shadow = texture2DCompare( shadowMap, shadowCoord.xy, shadowCoord.z );
   2982 </a><a href="#h3-0-1846" id="h3-0-1846" class="i">+		#endif
   2983 </a><a href="#h3-0-1847" id="h3-0-1847" class="i">+		}
   2984 </a><a href="#h3-0-1848" id="h3-0-1848" class="i">+		return mix( 1.0, shadow, shadowIntensity );
   2985 </a><a href="#h3-0-1849" id="h3-0-1849" class="i">+	}
   2986 </a><a href="#h3-0-1850" id="h3-0-1850" class="i">+	vec2 cubeToUV( vec3 v, float texelSizeY ) {
   2987 </a><a href="#h3-0-1851" id="h3-0-1851" class="i">+		vec3 absV = abs( v );
   2988 </a><a href="#h3-0-1852" id="h3-0-1852" class="i">+		float scaleToCube = 1.0 / max( absV.x, max( absV.y, absV.z ) );
   2989 </a><a href="#h3-0-1853" id="h3-0-1853" class="i">+		absV *= scaleToCube;
   2990 </a><a href="#h3-0-1854" id="h3-0-1854" class="i">+		v *= scaleToCube * ( 1.0 - 2.0 * texelSizeY );
   2991 </a><a href="#h3-0-1855" id="h3-0-1855" class="i">+		vec2 planar = v.xy;
   2992 </a><a href="#h3-0-1856" id="h3-0-1856" class="i">+		float almostATexel = 1.5 * texelSizeY;
   2993 </a><a href="#h3-0-1857" id="h3-0-1857" class="i">+		float almostOne = 1.0 - almostATexel;
   2994 </a><a href="#h3-0-1858" id="h3-0-1858" class="i">+		if ( absV.z &gt;= almostOne ) {
   2995 </a><a href="#h3-0-1859" id="h3-0-1859" class="i">+			if ( v.z &gt; 0.0 )
   2996 </a><a href="#h3-0-1860" id="h3-0-1860" class="i">+				planar.x = 4.0 - v.x;
   2997 </a><a href="#h3-0-1861" id="h3-0-1861" class="i">+		} else if ( absV.x &gt;= almostOne ) {
   2998 </a><a href="#h3-0-1862" id="h3-0-1862" class="i">+			float signX = sign( v.x );
   2999 </a><a href="#h3-0-1863" id="h3-0-1863" class="i">+			planar.x = v.z * signX + 2.0 * signX;
   3000 </a><a href="#h3-0-1864" id="h3-0-1864" class="i">+		} else if ( absV.y &gt;= almostOne ) {
   3001 </a><a href="#h3-0-1865" id="h3-0-1865" class="i">+			float signY = sign( v.y );
   3002 </a><a href="#h3-0-1866" id="h3-0-1866" class="i">+			planar.x = v.x + 2.0 * signY + 2.0;
   3003 </a><a href="#h3-0-1867" id="h3-0-1867" class="i">+			planar.y = v.z * signY - 2.0;
   3004 </a><a href="#h3-0-1868" id="h3-0-1868" class="i">+		}
   3005 </a><a href="#h3-0-1869" id="h3-0-1869" class="i">+		return vec2( 0.125, 0.25 ) * planar + vec2( 0.375, 0.75 );
   3006 </a><a href="#h3-0-1870" id="h3-0-1870" class="i">+	}
   3007 </a><a href="#h3-0-1871" id="h3-0-1871" class="i">+	float getPointShadow( sampler2D shadowMap, vec2 shadowMapSize, float shadowIntensity, float shadowBias, float shadowRadius, vec4 shadowCoord, float shadowCameraNear, float shadowCameraFar ) {
   3008 </a><a href="#h3-0-1872" id="h3-0-1872" class="i">+		float shadow = 1.0;
   3009 </a><a href="#h3-0-1873" id="h3-0-1873" class="i">+		vec3 lightToPosition = shadowCoord.xyz;
   3010 </a><a href="#h3-0-1874" id="h3-0-1874" class="i">+		
   3011 </a><a href="#h3-0-1875" id="h3-0-1875" class="i">+		float lightToPositionLength = length( lightToPosition );
   3012 </a><a href="#h3-0-1876" id="h3-0-1876" class="i">+		if ( lightToPositionLength - shadowCameraFar &lt;= 0.0 &amp;&amp; lightToPositionLength - shadowCameraNear &gt;= 0.0 ) {
   3013 </a><a href="#h3-0-1877" id="h3-0-1877" class="i">+			float dp = ( lightToPositionLength - shadowCameraNear ) / ( shadowCameraFar - shadowCameraNear );			dp += shadowBias;
   3014 </a><a href="#h3-0-1878" id="h3-0-1878" class="i">+			vec3 bd3D = normalize( lightToPosition );
   3015 </a><a href="#h3-0-1879" id="h3-0-1879" class="i">+			vec2 texelSize = vec2( 1.0 ) / ( shadowMapSize * vec2( 4.0, 2.0 ) );
   3016 </a><a href="#h3-0-1880" id="h3-0-1880" class="i">+			#if defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_PCF ) || defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_PCF_SOFT ) || defined( SHADOWMAP_TYPE_VSM )
   3017 </a><a href="#h3-0-1881" id="h3-0-1881" class="i">+				vec2 offset = vec2( - 1, 1 ) * shadowRadius * texelSize.y;
   3018 </a><a href="#h3-0-1882" id="h3-0-1882" class="i">+				shadow = (
   3019 </a><a href="#h3-0-1883" id="h3-0-1883" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.xyy, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3020 </a><a href="#h3-0-1884" id="h3-0-1884" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.yyy, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3021 </a><a href="#h3-0-1885" id="h3-0-1885" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.xyx, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3022 </a><a href="#h3-0-1886" id="h3-0-1886" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.yyx, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3023 </a><a href="#h3-0-1887" id="h3-0-1887" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3024 </a><a href="#h3-0-1888" id="h3-0-1888" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.xxy, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3025 </a><a href="#h3-0-1889" id="h3-0-1889" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.yxy, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3026 </a><a href="#h3-0-1890" id="h3-0-1890" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.xxx, texelSize.y ), dp ) +
   3027 </a><a href="#h3-0-1891" id="h3-0-1891" class="i">+					texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D + offset.yxx, texelSize.y ), dp )
   3028 </a><a href="#h3-0-1892" id="h3-0-1892" class="i">+				) * ( 1.0 / 9.0 );
   3029 </a><a href="#h3-0-1893" id="h3-0-1893" class="i">+			#else
   3030 </a><a href="#h3-0-1894" id="h3-0-1894" class="i">+				shadow = texture2DCompare( shadowMap, cubeToUV( bd3D, texelSize.y ), dp );
   3031 </a><a href="#h3-0-1895" id="h3-0-1895" class="i">+			#endif
   3032 </a><a href="#h3-0-1896" id="h3-0-1896" class="i">+		}
   3033 </a><a href="#h3-0-1897" id="h3-0-1897" class="i">+		return mix( 1.0, shadow, shadowIntensity );
   3034 </a><a href="#h3-0-1898" id="h3-0-1898" class="i">+	}
   3035 </a><a href="#h3-0-1899" id="h3-0-1899" class="i">+#endif`,XV=`#if NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_COORDS &gt; 0
   3036 </a><a href="#h3-0-1900" id="h3-0-1900" class="i">+	uniform mat4 spotLightMatrix[ NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_COORDS ];
   3037 </a><a href="#h3-0-1901" id="h3-0-1901" class="i">+	varying vec4 vSpotLightCoord[ NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_COORDS ];
   3038 </a><a href="#h3-0-1902" id="h3-0-1902" class="i">+#endif
   3039 </a><a href="#h3-0-1903" id="h3-0-1903" class="i">+#ifdef USE_SHADOWMAP
   3040 </a><a href="#h3-0-1904" id="h3-0-1904" class="i">+	#if NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0
   3041 </a><a href="#h3-0-1905" id="h3-0-1905" class="i">+		uniform mat4 directionalShadowMatrix[ NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3042 </a><a href="#h3-0-1906" id="h3-0-1906" class="i">+		varying vec4 vDirectionalShadowCoord[ NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3043 </a><a href="#h3-0-1907" id="h3-0-1907" class="i">+		struct DirectionalLightShadow {
   3044 </a><a href="#h3-0-1908" id="h3-0-1908" class="i">+			float shadowIntensity;
   3045 </a><a href="#h3-0-1909" id="h3-0-1909" class="i">+			float shadowBias;
   3046 </a><a href="#h3-0-1910" id="h3-0-1910" class="i">+			float shadowNormalBias;
   3047 </a><a href="#h3-0-1911" id="h3-0-1911" class="i">+			float shadowRadius;
   3048 </a><a href="#h3-0-1912" id="h3-0-1912" class="i">+			vec2 shadowMapSize;
   3049 </a><a href="#h3-0-1913" id="h3-0-1913" class="i">+		};
   3050 </a><a href="#h3-0-1914" id="h3-0-1914" class="i">+		uniform DirectionalLightShadow directionalLightShadows[ NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3051 </a><a href="#h3-0-1915" id="h3-0-1915" class="i">+	#endif
   3052 </a><a href="#h3-0-1916" id="h3-0-1916" class="i">+	#if NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0
   3053 </a><a href="#h3-0-1917" id="h3-0-1917" class="i">+		struct SpotLightShadow {
   3054 </a><a href="#h3-0-1918" id="h3-0-1918" class="i">+			float shadowIntensity;
   3055 </a><a href="#h3-0-1919" id="h3-0-1919" class="i">+			float shadowBias;
   3056 </a><a href="#h3-0-1920" id="h3-0-1920" class="i">+			float shadowNormalBias;
   3057 </a><a href="#h3-0-1921" id="h3-0-1921" class="i">+			float shadowRadius;
   3058 </a><a href="#h3-0-1922" id="h3-0-1922" class="i">+			vec2 shadowMapSize;
   3059 </a><a href="#h3-0-1923" id="h3-0-1923" class="i">+		};
   3060 </a><a href="#h3-0-1924" id="h3-0-1924" class="i">+		uniform SpotLightShadow spotLightShadows[ NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3061 </a><a href="#h3-0-1925" id="h3-0-1925" class="i">+	#endif
   3062 </a><a href="#h3-0-1926" id="h3-0-1926" class="i">+	#if NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0
   3063 </a><a href="#h3-0-1927" id="h3-0-1927" class="i">+		uniform mat4 pointShadowMatrix[ NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3064 </a><a href="#h3-0-1928" id="h3-0-1928" class="i">+		varying vec4 vPointShadowCoord[ NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3065 </a><a href="#h3-0-1929" id="h3-0-1929" class="i">+		struct PointLightShadow {
   3066 </a><a href="#h3-0-1930" id="h3-0-1930" class="i">+			float shadowIntensity;
   3067 </a><a href="#h3-0-1931" id="h3-0-1931" class="i">+			float shadowBias;
   3068 </a><a href="#h3-0-1932" id="h3-0-1932" class="i">+			float shadowNormalBias;
   3069 </a><a href="#h3-0-1933" id="h3-0-1933" class="i">+			float shadowRadius;
   3070 </a><a href="#h3-0-1934" id="h3-0-1934" class="i">+			vec2 shadowMapSize;
   3071 </a><a href="#h3-0-1935" id="h3-0-1935" class="i">+			float shadowCameraNear;
   3072 </a><a href="#h3-0-1936" id="h3-0-1936" class="i">+			float shadowCameraFar;
   3073 </a><a href="#h3-0-1937" id="h3-0-1937" class="i">+		};
   3074 </a><a href="#h3-0-1938" id="h3-0-1938" class="i">+		uniform PointLightShadow pointLightShadows[ NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS ];
   3075 </a><a href="#h3-0-1939" id="h3-0-1939" class="i">+	#endif
   3076 </a><a href="#h3-0-1940" id="h3-0-1940" class="i">+#endif`,qV=`#if ( defined( USE_SHADOWMAP ) &amp;&amp; ( NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0 || NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0 ) ) || ( NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_COORDS &gt; 0 )
   3077 </a><a href="#h3-0-1941" id="h3-0-1941" class="i">+	vec3 shadowWorldNormal = inverseTransformDirection( transformedNormal, viewMatrix );
   3078 </a><a href="#h3-0-1942" id="h3-0-1942" class="i">+	vec4 shadowWorldPosition;
   3079 </a><a href="#h3-0-1943" id="h3-0-1943" class="i">+#endif
   3080 </a><a href="#h3-0-1944" id="h3-0-1944" class="i">+#if defined( USE_SHADOWMAP )
   3081 </a><a href="#h3-0-1945" id="h3-0-1945" class="i">+	#if NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0
   3082 </a><a href="#h3-0-1946" id="h3-0-1946" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_start
   3083 </a><a href="#h3-0-1947" id="h3-0-1947" class="i">+		for ( int i = 0; i &lt; NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS; i ++ ) {
   3084 </a><a href="#h3-0-1948" id="h3-0-1948" class="i">+			shadowWorldPosition = worldPosition + vec4( shadowWorldNormal * directionalLightShadows[ i ].shadowNormalBias, 0 );
   3085 </a><a href="#h3-0-1949" id="h3-0-1949" class="i">+			vDirectionalShadowCoord[ i ] = directionalShadowMatrix[ i ] * shadowWorldPosition;
   3086 </a><a href="#h3-0-1950" id="h3-0-1950" class="i">+		}
   3087 </a><a href="#h3-0-1951" id="h3-0-1951" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_end
   3088 </a><a href="#h3-0-1952" id="h3-0-1952" class="i">+	#endif
   3089 </a><a href="#h3-0-1953" id="h3-0-1953" class="i">+	#if NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0
   3090 </a><a href="#h3-0-1954" id="h3-0-1954" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_start
   3091 </a><a href="#h3-0-1955" id="h3-0-1955" class="i">+		for ( int i = 0; i &lt; NUM_POINT_LIGHT_SHADOWS; i ++ ) {
   3092 </a><a href="#h3-0-1956" id="h3-0-1956" class="i">+			shadowWorldPosition = worldPosition + vec4( shadowWorldNormal * pointLightShadows[ i ].shadowNormalBias, 0 );
   3093 </a><a href="#h3-0-1957" id="h3-0-1957" class="i">+			vPointShadowCoord[ i ] = pointShadowMatrix[ i ] * shadowWorldPosition;
   3094 </a><a href="#h3-0-1958" id="h3-0-1958" class="i">+		}
   3095 </a><a href="#h3-0-1959" id="h3-0-1959" class="i">+		#pragma unroll_loop_end
   3096 </a><a href="#h3-0-1960" id="h3-0-1960" class="i">+	#endif
   3097 </a><a href="#h3-0-1961" id="h3-0-1961" class="i">+#endif
   3098 </a><a href="#h3-0-1962" id="h3-0-1962" class="i">+#if NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_COORDS &gt; 0
   3099 </a><a href="#h3-0-1963" id="h3-0-1963" class="i">+	#pragma unroll_loop_start
   3100 </a><a href="#h3-0-1964" id="h3-0-1964" class="i">+	for ( int i = 0; i &lt; NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_COORDS; i ++ ) {
   3101 </a><a href="#h3-0-1965" id="h3-0-1965" class="i">+		shadowWorldPosition = worldPosition;
   3102 </a><a href="#h3-0-1966" id="h3-0-1966" class="i">+		#if ( defined( USE_SHADOWMAP ) &amp;&amp; UNROLLED_LOOP_INDEX &lt; NUM_SPOT_LIGHT_SHADOWS )
   3103 </a><a href="#h3-0-1967" id="h3-0-1967" class="i">+			shadowWorldPosition.xyz += shadowWorldNormal * spotLightShadows[ i ].shadowNormalBias;
   3104 </a><a href="#h3-0-1968" id="h3-0-1968" class="i">+		#endif
   3105 </a><a href="#h3-0-1969" id="h3-0-1969" class="i">+		vSpotLightCoord[ i ] = spotLightMatrix[ i ] * shadowWorldPosition;
   3106 </a><a href="#h3-0-1970" id="h3-0-1970" class="i">+	}
   3107 </a><a href="#h3-0-1971" id="h3-0-1971" class="i">+	#pragma unroll_loop_end
   3108 </a><a href="#h3-0-1972" id="h3-0-1972" class="i">+#endif`,YV=`float getShadowMask() {
   3109 </a><a href="#h3-0-1973" id="h3-0-1973" class="i">+	float shadow = 1.0;
   3110 </a><a href="#h3-0-1974" id="h3-0-1974" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_SHADOWMAP
   3111 </a><a href="#h3-0-1975" id="h3-0-1975" class="i">+	#if NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS &gt; 0
   3112 </a><a href="#h3-0-1976" id="h3-0-1976" class="i">+	DirectionalLightShadow directionalLight;
   3113 </a><a href="#h3-0-1977" id="h3-0-1977" class="i">+	#pragma unroll_loop_start
   3114 </a><a href="#h3-0-1978" id="h3-0-1978" class="i">+	for ( int i = 0; i &lt; NUM_DIR_LIGHT_SHADOWS; i ++ ) {
   3115 </a><a href="#h3-0-1979" id="h3-0-1979" class="i">+		directionalLight = directionalLightShadows[ i ];
   3116 </a><a href="#h3-0-1980" id="h3-0-1980" class="i">+		shadow *= receiveShadow ? getShadow( directionalShadowMap[ i ], directionalLight.shadowMapSize, directionalLight.shadowIntensity, directionalLight.shadowBias, directionalLight.shadowRadius, vDirectionalShadowCoord[ i ] ) : 1.0;
   3117 </a><a href="#h3-0-1981" id="h3-0-1981" class="i">+	}
   3118 </a><a href="#h3-0-1982" id="h3-0-1982" class="i">+	#pragma unroll_loop_end

   3235 </a><a href="#h3-0-2099" id="h3-0-2099" class="i">+vec3 agxDefaultContrastApprox( vec3 x ) {
   3236 </a><a href="#h3-0-2100" id="h3-0-2100" class="i">+	vec3 x2 = x * x;

   3271 </a><a href="#h3-0-2135" id="h3-0-2135" class="i">+vec3 NeutralToneMapping( vec3 color ) {
   3272 </a><a href="#h3-0-2136" id="h3-0-2136" class="i">+	const float StartCompression = 0.8 - 0.04;
   3273 </a><a href="#h3-0-2137" id="h3-0-2137" class="i">+	const float Desaturation = 0.15;
   3274 </a><a href="#h3-0-2138" id="h3-0-2138" class="i">+	color *= toneMappingExposure;
   3275 </a><a href="#h3-0-2139" id="h3-0-2139" class="i">+	float x = min( color.r, min( color.g, color.b ) );
   3276 </a><a href="#h3-0-2140" id="h3-0-2140" class="i">+	float offset = x &lt; 0.08 ? x - 6.25 * x * x : 0.04;
   3277 </a><a href="#h3-0-2141" id="h3-0-2141" class="i">+	color -= offset;
   3278 </a><a href="#h3-0-2142" id="h3-0-2142" class="i">+	float peak = max( color.r, max( color.g, color.b ) );
   3279 </a><a href="#h3-0-2143" id="h3-0-2143" class="i">+	if ( peak &lt; StartCompression ) return color;
   3280 </a><a href="#h3-0-2144" id="h3-0-2144" class="i">+	float d = 1. - StartCompression;
   3281 </a><a href="#h3-0-2145" id="h3-0-2145" class="i">+	float newPeak = 1. - d * d / ( peak + d - StartCompression );
   3282 </a><a href="#h3-0-2146" id="h3-0-2146" class="i">+	color *= newPeak / peak;
   3283 </a><a href="#h3-0-2147" id="h3-0-2147" class="i">+	float g = 1. - 1. / ( Desaturation * ( peak - newPeak ) + 1. );
   3284 </a><a href="#h3-0-2148" id="h3-0-2148" class="i">+	return mix( color, vec3( newPeak ), g );
   3285 </a><a href="#h3-0-2149" id="h3-0-2149" class="i">+}
   3286 </a><a href="#h3-0-2150" id="h3-0-2150" class="i">+vec3 CustomToneMapping( vec3 color ) { return color; }`,t6=`#ifdef USE_TRANSMISSION

   3303 </a><a href="#h3-0-2167" id="h3-0-2167" class="i">+		pos, modelMatrix, viewMatrix, projectionMatrix, material.dispersion, material.ior, material.thickness,

   3308 </a><a href="#h3-0-2172" id="h3-0-2172" class="i">+	uniform float transmission;

   3317 </a><a href="#h3-0-2181" id="h3-0-2181" class="i">+	#endif
   3318 </a><a href="#h3-0-2182" id="h3-0-2182" class="i">+	uniform vec2 transmissionSamplerSize;
   3319 </a><a href="#h3-0-2183" id="h3-0-2183" class="i">+	uniform sampler2D transmissionSamplerMap;
   3320 </a><a href="#h3-0-2184" id="h3-0-2184" class="i">+	uniform mat4 modelMatrix;
   3321 </a><a href="#h3-0-2185" id="h3-0-2185" class="i">+	uniform mat4 projectionMatrix;
   3322 </a><a href="#h3-0-2186" id="h3-0-2186" class="i">+	varying vec3 vWorldPosition;
   3323 </a><a href="#h3-0-2187" id="h3-0-2187" class="i">+	float w0( float a ) {
   3324 </a><a href="#h3-0-2188" id="h3-0-2188" class="i">+		return ( 1.0 / 6.0 ) * ( a * ( a * ( - a + 3.0 ) - 3.0 ) + 1.0 );
   3325 </a><a href="#h3-0-2189" id="h3-0-2189" class="i">+	}
   3326 </a><a href="#h3-0-2190" id="h3-0-2190" class="i">+	float w1( float a ) {
   3327 </a><a href="#h3-0-2191" id="h3-0-2191" class="i">+		return ( 1.0 / 6.0 ) * ( a *  a * ( 3.0 * a - 6.0 ) + 4.0 );
   3328 </a><a href="#h3-0-2192" id="h3-0-2192" class="i">+	}
   3329 </a><a href="#h3-0-2193" id="h3-0-2193" class="i">+	float w2( float a ){
   3330 </a><a href="#h3-0-2194" id="h3-0-2194" class="i">+		return ( 1.0 / 6.0 ) * ( a * ( a * ( - 3.0 * a + 3.0 ) + 3.0 ) + 1.0 );
   3331 </a><a href="#h3-0-2195" id="h3-0-2195" class="i">+	}
   3332 </a><a href="#h3-0-2196" id="h3-0-2196" class="i">+	float w3( float a ) {
   3333 </a><a href="#h3-0-2197" id="h3-0-2197" class="i">+		return ( 1.0 / 6.0 ) * ( a * a * a );
   3334 </a><a href="#h3-0-2198" id="h3-0-2198" class="i">+	}
   3335 </a><a href="#h3-0-2199" id="h3-0-2199" class="i">+	float g0( float a ) {
   3336 </a><a href="#h3-0-2200" id="h3-0-2200" class="i">+		return w0( a ) + w1( a );
   3337 </a><a href="#h3-0-2201" id="h3-0-2201" class="i">+	}
   3338 </a><a href="#h3-0-2202" id="h3-0-2202" class="i">+	float g1( float a ) {
   3339 </a><a href="#h3-0-2203" id="h3-0-2203" class="i">+		return w2( a ) + w3( a );
   3340 </a><a href="#h3-0-2204" id="h3-0-2204" class="i">+	}
   3341 </a><a href="#h3-0-2205" id="h3-0-2205" class="i">+	float h0( float a ) {
   3342 </a><a href="#h3-0-2206" id="h3-0-2206" class="i">+		return - 1.0 + w1( a ) / ( w0( a ) + w1( a ) );
   3343 </a><a href="#h3-0-2207" id="h3-0-2207" class="i">+	}
   3344 </a><a href="#h3-0-2208" id="h3-0-2208" class="i">+	float h1( float a ) {
   3345 </a><a href="#h3-0-2209" id="h3-0-2209" class="i">+		return 1.0 + w3( a ) / ( w2( a ) + w3( a ) );
   3346 </a><a href="#h3-0-2210" id="h3-0-2210" class="i">+	}
   3347 </a><a href="#h3-0-2211" id="h3-0-2211" class="i">+	vec4 bicubic( sampler2D tex, vec2 uv, vec4 texelSize, float lod ) {
   3348 </a><a href="#h3-0-2212" id="h3-0-2212" class="i">+		uv = uv * texelSize.zw + 0.5;
   3349 </a><a href="#h3-0-2213" id="h3-0-2213" class="i">+		vec2 iuv = floor( uv );
   3350 </a><a href="#h3-0-2214" id="h3-0-2214" class="i">+		vec2 fuv = fract( uv );
   3351 </a><a href="#h3-0-2215" id="h3-0-2215" class="i">+		float g0x = g0( fuv.x );
   3352 </a><a href="#h3-0-2216" id="h3-0-2216" class="i">+		float g1x = g1( fuv.x );
   3353 </a><a href="#h3-0-2217" id="h3-0-2217" class="i">+		float h0x = h0( fuv.x );
   3354 </a><a href="#h3-0-2218" id="h3-0-2218" class="i">+		float h1x = h1( fuv.x );
   3355 </a><a href="#h3-0-2219" id="h3-0-2219" class="i">+		float h0y = h0( fuv.y );
   3356 </a><a href="#h3-0-2220" id="h3-0-2220" class="i">+		float h1y = h1( fuv.y );
   3357 </a><a href="#h3-0-2221" id="h3-0-2221" class="i">+		vec2 p0 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h0x, iuv.y + h0y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   3358 </a><a href="#h3-0-2222" id="h3-0-2222" class="i">+		vec2 p1 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h1x, iuv.y + h0y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   3359 </a><a href="#h3-0-2223" id="h3-0-2223" class="i">+		vec2 p2 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h0x, iuv.y + h1y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   3360 </a><a href="#h3-0-2224" id="h3-0-2224" class="i">+		vec2 p3 = ( vec2( iuv.x + h1x, iuv.y + h1y ) - 0.5 ) * texelSize.xy;
   3361 </a><a href="#h3-0-2225" id="h3-0-2225" class="i">+		return g0( fuv.y ) * ( g0x * textureLod( tex, p0, lod ) + g1x * textureLod( tex, p1, lod ) ) +
   3362 </a><a href="#h3-0-2226" id="h3-0-2226" class="i">+			g1( fuv.y ) * ( g0x * textureLod( tex, p2, lod ) + g1x * textureLod( tex, p3, lod ) );
   3363 </a><a href="#h3-0-2227" id="h3-0-2227" class="i">+	}
   3364 </a><a href="#h3-0-2228" id="h3-0-2228" class="i">+	vec4 textureBicubic( sampler2D sampler, vec2 uv, float lod ) {
   3365 </a><a href="#h3-0-2229" id="h3-0-2229" class="i">+		vec2 fLodSize = vec2( textureSize( sampler, int( lod ) ) );
   3366 </a><a href="#h3-0-2230" id="h3-0-2230" class="i">+		vec2 cLodSize = vec2( textureSize( sampler, int( lod + 1.0 ) ) );
   3367 </a><a href="#h3-0-2231" id="h3-0-2231" class="i">+		vec2 fLodSizeInv = 1.0 / fLodSize;
   3368 </a><a href="#h3-0-2232" id="h3-0-2232" class="i">+		vec2 cLodSizeInv = 1.0 / cLodSize;
   3369 </a><a href="#h3-0-2233" id="h3-0-2233" class="i">+		vec4 fSample = bicubic( sampler, uv, vec4( fLodSizeInv, fLodSize ), floor( lod ) );
   3370 </a><a href="#h3-0-2234" id="h3-0-2234" class="i">+		vec4 cSample = bicubic( sampler, uv, vec4( cLodSizeInv, cLodSize ), ceil( lod ) );
   3371 </a><a href="#h3-0-2235" id="h3-0-2235" class="i">+		return mix( fSample, cSample, fract( lod ) );
   3372 </a><a href="#h3-0-2236" id="h3-0-2236" class="i">+	}
   3373 </a><a href="#h3-0-2237" id="h3-0-2237" class="i">+	vec3 getVolumeTransmissionRay( const in vec3 n, const in vec3 v, const in float thickness, const in float ior, const in mat4 modelMatrix ) {
   3374 </a><a href="#h3-0-2238" id="h3-0-2238" class="i">+		vec3 refractionVector = refract( - v, normalize( n ), 1.0 / ior );
   3375 </a><a href="#h3-0-2239" id="h3-0-2239" class="i">+		vec3 modelScale;
   3376 </a><a href="#h3-0-2240" id="h3-0-2240" class="i">+		modelScale.x = length( vec3( modelMatrix[ 0 ].xyz ) );
   3377 </a><a href="#h3-0-2241" id="h3-0-2241" class="i">+		modelScale.y = length( vec3( modelMatrix[ 1 ].xyz ) );
   3378 </a><a href="#h3-0-2242" id="h3-0-2242" class="i">+		modelScale.z = length( vec3( modelMatrix[ 2 ].xyz ) );
   3379 </a><a href="#h3-0-2243" id="h3-0-2243" class="i">+		return normalize( refractionVector ) * thickness * modelScale;
   3380 </a><a href="#h3-0-2244" id="h3-0-2244" class="i">+	}
   3381 </a><a href="#h3-0-2245" id="h3-0-2245" class="i">+	float applyIorToRoughness( const in float roughness, const in float ior ) {
   3382 </a><a href="#h3-0-2246" id="h3-0-2246" class="i">+		return roughness * clamp( ior * 2.0 - 2.0, 0.0, 1.0 );
   3383 </a><a href="#h3-0-2247" id="h3-0-2247" class="i">+	}
   3384 </a><a href="#h3-0-2248" id="h3-0-2248" class="i">+	vec4 getTransmissionSample( const in vec2 fragCoord, const in float roughness, const in float ior ) {
   3385 </a><a href="#h3-0-2249" id="h3-0-2249" class="i">+		float lod = log2( transmissionSamplerSize.x ) * applyIorToRoughness( roughness, ior );
   3386 </a><a href="#h3-0-2250" id="h3-0-2250" class="i">+		return textureBicubic( transmissionSamplerMap, fragCoord.xy, lod );
   3387 </a><a href="#h3-0-2251" id="h3-0-2251" class="i">+	}
   3388 </a><a href="#h3-0-2252" id="h3-0-2252" class="i">+	vec3 volumeAttenuation( const in float transmissionDistance, const in vec3 attenuationColor, const in float attenuationDistance ) {
   3389 </a><a href="#h3-0-2253" id="h3-0-2253" class="i">+		if ( isinf( attenuationDistance ) ) {
   3390 </a><a href="#h3-0-2254" id="h3-0-2254" class="i">+			return vec3( 1.0 );
   3391 </a><a href="#h3-0-2255" id="h3-0-2255" class="i">+		} else {
   3392 </a><a href="#h3-0-2256" id="h3-0-2256" class="i">+			vec3 attenuationCoefficient = -log( attenuationColor ) / attenuationDistance;
   3393 </a><a href="#h3-0-2257" id="h3-0-2257" class="i">+			vec3 transmittance = exp( - attenuationCoefficient * transmissionDistance );			return transmittance;
   3394 </a><a href="#h3-0-2258" id="h3-0-2258" class="i">+		}
   3395 </a><a href="#h3-0-2259" id="h3-0-2259" class="i">+	}
   3396 </a><a href="#h3-0-2260" id="h3-0-2260" class="i">+	vec4 getIBLVolumeRefraction( const in vec3 n, const in vec3 v, const in float roughness, const in vec3 diffuseColor,
   3397 </a><a href="#h3-0-2261" id="h3-0-2261" class="i">+		const in vec3 specularColor, const in float specularF90, const in vec3 position, const in mat4 modelMatrix,
   3398 </a><a href="#h3-0-2262" id="h3-0-2262" class="i">+		const in mat4 viewMatrix, const in mat4 projMatrix, const in float dispersion, const in float ior, const in float thickness,
   3399 </a><a href="#h3-0-2263" id="h3-0-2263" class="i">+		const in vec3 attenuationColor, const in float attenuationDistance ) {
   3400 </a><a href="#h3-0-2264" id="h3-0-2264" class="i">+		vec4 transmittedLight;
   3401 </a><a href="#h3-0-2265" id="h3-0-2265" class="i">+		vec3 transmittance;
   3402 </a><a href="#h3-0-2266" id="h3-0-2266" class="i">+		#ifdef USE_DISPERSION
   3403 </a><a href="#h3-0-2267" id="h3-0-2267" class="i">+			float halfSpread = ( ior - 1.0 ) * 0.025 * dispersion;
   3404 </a><a href="#h3-0-2268" id="h3-0-2268" class="i">+			vec3 iors = vec3( ior - halfSpread, ior, ior + halfSpread );
   3405 </a><a href="#h3-0-2269" id="h3-0-2269" class="i">+			for ( int i = 0; i &lt; 3; i ++ ) {
   3406 </a><a href="#h3-0-2270" id="h3-0-2270" class="i">+				vec3 transmissionRay = getVolumeTransmissionRay( n, v, thickness, iors[ i ], modelMatrix );
   3407 </a><a href="#h3-0-2271" id="h3-0-2271" class="i">+				vec3 refractedRayExit = position + transmissionRay;
   3408 </a><a href="#h3-0-2272" id="h3-0-2272" class="i">+				vec4 ndcPos = projMatrix * viewMatrix * vec4( refractedRayExit, 1.0 );
   3409 </a><a href="#h3-0-2273" id="h3-0-2273" class="i">+				vec2 refractionCoords = ndcPos.xy / ndcPos.w;
   3410 </a><a href="#h3-0-2274" id="h3-0-2274" class="i">+				refractionCoords += 1.0;
   3411 </a><a href="#h3-0-2275" id="h3-0-2275" class="i">+				refractionCoords /= 2.0;
   3412 </a><a href="#h3-0-2276" id="h3-0-2276" class="i">+				vec4 transmissionSample = getTransmissionSample( refractionCoords, roughness, iors[ i ] );
   3413 </a><a href="#h3-0-2277" id="h3-0-2277" class="i">+				transmittedLight[ i ] = transmissionSample[ i ];
   3414 </a><a href="#h3-0-2278" id="h3-0-2278" class="i">+				transmittedLight.a += transmissionSample.a;
   3415 </a><a href="#h3-0-2279" id="h3-0-2279" class="i">+				transmittance[ i ] = diffuseColor[ i ] * volumeAttenuation( length( transmissionRay ), attenuationColor, attenuationDistance )[ i ];
   3416 </a><a href="#h3-0-2280" id="h3-0-2280" class="i">+			}
   3417 </a><a href="#h3-0-2281" id="h3-0-2281" class="i">+			transmittedLight.a /= 3.0;
   3418 </a><a href="#h3-0-2282" id="h3-0-2282" class="i">+		#else
   3419 </a><a href="#h3-0-2283" id="h3-0-2283" class="i">+			vec3 transmissionRay = getVolumeTransmissionRay( n, v, thickness, ior, modelMatrix );
   3420 </a><a href="#h3-0-2284" id="h3-0-2284" class="i">+			vec3 refractedRayExit = position + transmissionRay;
   3421 </a><a href="#h3-0-2285" id="h3-0-2285" class="i">+			vec4 ndcPos = projMatrix * viewMatrix * vec4( refractedRayExit, 1.0 );
   3422 </a><a href="#h3-0-2286" id="h3-0-2286" class="i">+			vec2 refractionCoords = ndcPos.xy / ndcPos.w;
   3423 </a><a href="#h3-0-2287" id="h3-0-2287" class="i">+			refractionCoords += 1.0;
   3424 </a><a href="#h3-0-2288" id="h3-0-2288" class="i">+			refractionCoords /= 2.0;
   3425 </a><a href="#h3-0-2289" id="h3-0-2289" class="i">+			transmittedLight = getTransmissionSample( refractionCoords, roughness, ior );
   3426 </a><a href="#h3-0-2290" id="h3-0-2290" class="i">+			transmittance = diffuseColor * volumeAttenuation( length( transmissionRay ), attenuationColor, attenuationDistance );
   3427 </a><a href="#h3-0-2291" id="h3-0-2291" class="i">+		#endif
   3428 </a><a href="#h3-0-2292" id="h3-0-2292" class="i">+		vec3 attenuatedColor = transmittance * transmittedLight.rgb;
   3429 </a><a href="#h3-0-2293" id="h3-0-2293" class="i">+		vec3 F = EnvironmentBRDF( n, v, specularColor, specularF90, roughness );
   3430 </a><a href="#h3-0-2294" id="h3-0-2294" class="i">+		float transmittanceFactor = ( transmittance.r + transmittance.g + transmittance.b ) / 3.0;
   3431 </a><a href="#h3-0-2295" id="h3-0-2295" class="i">+		return vec4( ( 1.0 - F ) * attenuatedColor, 1.0 - ( 1.0 - transmittedLight.a ) * transmittanceFactor );
   3432 </a><a href="#h3-0-2296" id="h3-0-2296" class="i">+	}
   3433 </a><a href="#h3-0-2297" id="h3-0-2297" class="i">+#endif`,n6=`#if defined( USE_UV ) || defined( USE_ANISOTROPY )
   3434 </a><a href="#h3-0-2298" id="h3-0-2298" class="i">+	varying vec2 vUv;
   3435 </a><a href="#h3-0-2299" id="h3-0-2299" class="i">+#endif
   3436 </a><a href="#h3-0-2300" id="h3-0-2300" class="i">+#ifdef USE_MAP
   3437 </a><a href="#h3-0-2301" id="h3-0-2301" class="i">+	varying vec2 vMapUv;
   3438 </a><a href="#h3-0-2302" id="h3-0-2302" class="i">+#endif
   3439 </a><a href="#h3-0-2303" id="h3-0-2303" class="i">+#ifdef USE_ALPHAMAP
   3440 </a><a href="#h3-0-2304" id="h3-0-2304" class="i">+	varying vec2 vAlphaMapUv;
   3441 </a><a href="#h3-0-2305" id="h3-0-2305" class="i">+#endif
   3442 </a><a href="#h3-0-2306" id="h3-0-2306" class="i">+#ifdef USE_LIGHTMAP
   3443 </a><a href="#h3-0-2307" id="h3-0-2307" class="i">+	varying vec2 vLightMapUv;
   3444 </a><a href="#h3-0-2308" id="h3-0-2308" class="i">+#endif
   3445 </a><a href="#h3-0-2309" id="h3-0-2309" class="i">+#ifdef USE_AOMAP
   3446 </a><a href="#h3-0-2310" id="h3-0-2310" class="i">+	varying vec2 vAoMapUv;
   3447 </a><a href="#h3-0-2311" id="h3-0-2311" class="i">+#endif
   3448 </a><a href="#h3-0-2312" id="h3-0-2312" class="i">+#ifdef USE_BUMPMAP

   4461 </a><a href="#h3-0-3325" id="h3-0-3325" class="i">+	vec3 totalEmissiveRadiance = emissive;

   4483 </a><a href="#h3-0-3347" id="h3-0-3347" class="i">+	vec3 outgoingLight = totalDiffuse + totalSpecular + totalEmissiveRadiance;
   4484 </a><a href="#h3-0-3348" id="h3-0-3348" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_SHEEN

   4486 </a><a href="#h3-0-3350" id="h3-0-3350" class="i">+		outgoingLight = outgoingLight * sheenEnergyComp + sheenSpecularDirect + sheenSpecularIndirect;
   4487 </a><a href="#h3-0-3351" id="h3-0-3351" class="i">+	#endif
   4488 </a><a href="#h3-0-3352" id="h3-0-3352" class="i">+	#ifdef USE_CLEARCOAT
   4489 </a><a href="#h3-0-3353" id="h3-0-3353" class="i">+		float dotNVcc = saturate( dot( geometryClearcoatNormal, geometryViewDir ) );
   4490 </a><a href="#h3-0-3354" id="h3-0-3354" class="i">+		vec3 Fcc = F_Schlick( material.clearcoatF0, material.clearcoatF90, dotNVcc );
   4491 </a><a href="#h3-0-3355" id="h3-0-3355" class="i">+		outgoingLight = outgoingLight * ( 1.0 - material.clearcoat * Fcc ) + ( clearcoatSpecularDirect + clearcoatSpecularIndirect ) * material.clearcoat;
   4492 </a><a href="#h3-0-3356" id="h3-0-3356" class="i">+	#endif
   4493 </a><a href="#h3-0-3357" id="h3-0-3357" class="i">+	#include &lt;opaque_fragment&gt;

   5507 </a><a href="#h4-0-408" id="h4-0-408" class="i">+
   5508 </a><a href="#h4-0-409" id="h4-0-409" class="i">+struct LightResult {
   5509 </a><a href="#h4-0-410" id="h4-0-410" class="i">+  float specular;
   5510 </a><a href="#h4-0-411" id="h4-0-411" class="i">+  float diffuse;
   5511 </a><a href="#h4-0-412" id="h4-0-412" class="i">+};
   5512 </a><a href="#h4-0-413" id="h4-0-413" class="i">+
   5513 </a><a href="#h4-0-414" id="h4-0-414" class="i">+float _phongSpecular(
   5514 </a><a href="#h4-0-415" id="h4-0-415" class="i">+  vec3 lightDirection,
   5515 </a><a href="#h4-0-416" id="h4-0-416" class="i">+  vec3 viewDirection,
   5516 </a><a href="#h4-0-417" id="h4-0-417" class="i">+  vec3 surfaceNormal,
   5517 </a><a href="#h4-0-418" id="h4-0-418" class="i">+  float shininess) {
   5518 </a><a href="#h4-0-419" id="h4-0-419" class="i">+
   5519 </a><a href="#h4-0-420" id="h4-0-420" class="i">+  vec3 R = reflect(lightDirection, surfaceNormal);
   5520 </a><a href="#h4-0-421" id="h4-0-421" class="i">+  return pow(max(0.0, dot(R, viewDirection)), shininess);
   5521 </a><a href="#h4-0-422" id="h4-0-422" class="i">+}
   5522 </a><a href="#h4-0-423" id="h4-0-423" class="i">+
   5523 </a><a href="#h4-0-424" id="h4-0-424" class="i">+float _lambertDiffuse(vec3 lightDirection, vec3 surfaceNormal) {
   5524 </a><a href="#h4-0-425" id="h4-0-425" class="i">+  return max(0.0, dot(-lightDirection, surfaceNormal));
   5525 </a><a href="#h4-0-426" id="h4-0-426" class="i">+}
   5526 </a><a href="#h4-0-427" id="h4-0-427" class="i">+
   5527 </a><a href="#h4-0-428" id="h4-0-428" class="i">+LightResult _light(vec3 viewDirection, vec3 normal, vec3 lightVector, float shininess, float metallic) {
   5528 </a><a href="#h4-0-429" id="h4-0-429" class="i">+
   5529 </a><a href="#h4-0-430" id="h4-0-430" class="i">+  vec3 lightDir = normalize(lightVector);
   5530 </a><a href="#h4-0-431" id="h4-0-431" class="i">+
   5531 </a><a href="#h4-0-432" id="h4-0-432" class="i">+  //compute our diffuse &amp; specular terms
   5532 </a><a href="#h4-0-433" id="h4-0-433" class="i">+  LightResult lr;
   5533 </a><a href="#h4-0-434" id="h4-0-434" class="i">+  float specularIntensity = mix(1.0, 0.4, metallic);
   5534 </a><a href="#h4-0-435" id="h4-0-435" class="i">+  float diffuseIntensity = mix(1.0, 0.1, metallic);
   5535 </a><a href="#h4-0-436" id="h4-0-436" class="i">+  if (uSpecular)
   5536 </a><a href="#h4-0-437" id="h4-0-437" class="i">+    lr.specular = (_phongSpecular(lightDir, viewDirection, normal, shininess)) * specularIntensity;
   5537 </a><a href="#h4-0-438" id="h4-0-438" class="i">+    lr.diffuse = _lambertDiffuse(lightDir, normal) * diffuseIntensity;
   5538 </a><a href="#h4-0-439" id="h4-0-439" class="i">+  return lr;
   5539 </a><a href="#h4-0-440" id="h4-0-440" class="i">+}
   5540 </a><a href="#h4-0-441" id="h4-0-441" class="i">+
   5541 </a><a href="#h4-0-442" id="h4-0-442" class="i">+// converts the range of &quot;value&quot; from [min1 to max1] to [min2 to max2]
   5542 </a><a href="#h4-0-443" id="h4-0-443" class="i">+float map(float value, float min1, float max1, float min2, float max2) {
   5543 </a><a href="#h4-0-444" id="h4-0-444" class="i">+  return min2 + (value - min1) * (max2 - min2) / (max1 - min1);
   5544 </a><a href="#h4-0-445" id="h4-0-445" class="i">+}
   5545 </a><a href="#h4-0-446" id="h4-0-446" class="i">+
   5546 </a><a href="#h4-0-447" id="h4-0-447" class="i">+vec2 mapTextureToNormal( vec3 v ){
   5547 </a><a href="#h4-0-448" id="h4-0-448" class="i">+  // x = r sin(phi) cos(theta)   
   5548 </a><a href="#h4-0-449" id="h4-0-449" class="i">+  // y = r cos(phi)  
   5549 </a><a href="#h4-0-450" id="h4-0-450" class="i">+  // z = r sin(phi) sin(theta)
   5550 </a><a href="#h4-0-451" id="h4-0-451" class="i">+  float phi = acos( v.y );
   5551 </a><a href="#h4-0-452" id="h4-0-452" class="i">+  // if phi is 0, then there are no x, z components
   5552 </a><a href="#h4-0-453" id="h4-0-453" class="i">+  float theta = 0.0;
   5553 </a><a href="#h4-0-454" id="h4-0-454" class="i">+  // else 
   5554 </a><a href="#h4-0-455" id="h4-0-455" class="i">+  theta = acos(v.x / sin(phi));
   5555 </a><a href="#h4-0-456" id="h4-0-456" class="i">+  float sinTheta = v.z / sin(phi);
   5556 </a><a href="#h4-0-457" id="h4-0-457" class="i">+  if (sinTheta &lt; 0.0) {
   5557 </a><a href="#h4-0-458" id="h4-0-458" class="i">+    // Turn it into -theta, but in the 0-2PI range
   5558 </a><a href="#h4-0-459" id="h4-0-459" class="i">+    theta = 2.0 * PI - theta;
   5559 </a><a href="#h4-0-460" id="h4-0-460" class="i">+  }
   5560 </a><a href="#h4-0-461" id="h4-0-461" class="i">+  theta = theta / (2.0 * 3.14159);
   5561 </a><a href="#h4-0-462" id="h4-0-462" class="i">+  phi = phi / 3.14159 ;
   5562 </a><a href="#h4-0-463" id="h4-0-463" class="i">+  
   5563 </a><a href="#h4-0-464" id="h4-0-464" class="i">+  vec2 angles = vec2( fract(theta + 0.25), 1.0 - phi );
   5564 </a><a href="#h4-0-465" id="h4-0-465" class="i">+  return angles;
   5565 </a><a href="#h4-0-466" id="h4-0-466" class="i">+}
   5566 </a><a href="#h4-0-467" id="h4-0-467" class="i">+
   5567 </a><a href="#h4-0-468" id="h4-0-468" class="i">+
   5568 </a><a href="#h4-0-469" id="h4-0-469" class="i">+vec3 calculateImageDiffuse(vec3 vNormal, vec3 vViewPosition, float metallic){
   5569 </a><a href="#h4-0-470" id="h4-0-470" class="i">+  // make 2 seperate builds 
   5570 </a><a href="#h4-0-471" id="h4-0-471" class="i">+  vec3 worldCameraPosition =  vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0);  // hardcoded world camera position
   5571 </a><a href="#h4-0-472" id="h4-0-472" class="i">+  vec3 worldNormal = normalize(vNormal * uCameraRotation);
   5572 </a><a href="#h4-0-473" id="h4-0-473" class="i">+  vec2 newTexCoor = mapTextureToNormal( worldNormal );
   5573 </a><a href="#h4-0-474" id="h4-0-474" class="i">+  vec4 texture = TEXTURE( environmentMapDiffused, newTexCoor );
   5574 </a><a href="#h4-0-475" id="h4-0-475" class="i">+  // this is to make the darker sections more dark
   5575 </a><a href="#h4-0-476" id="h4-0-476" class="i">+  // png and jpg usually flatten the brightness so it is to reverse that
   5576 </a><a href="#h4-0-477" id="h4-0-477" class="i">+  return mix(smoothstep(vec3(0.0), vec3(1.0), texture.xyz), vec3(0.0), metallic);
   5577 </a><a href="#h4-0-478" id="h4-0-478" class="i">+}
   5578 </a><a href="#h4-0-479" id="h4-0-479" class="i">+
   5579 </a><a href="#h4-0-480" id="h4-0-480" class="i">+vec3 calculateImageSpecular(vec3 vNormal, vec3 vViewPosition, float shininess, float metallic){
   5580 </a><a href="#h4-0-481" id="h4-0-481" class="i">+  vec3 worldCameraPosition =  vec3(0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
   5581 </a><a href="#h4-0-482" id="h4-0-482" class="i">+  vec3 worldNormal = normalize(vNormal);
   5582 </a><a href="#h4-0-483" id="h4-0-483" class="i">+  vec3 lightDirection = normalize( vViewPosition - worldCameraPosition );
   5583 </a><a href="#h4-0-484" id="h4-0-484" class="i">+  vec3 R = reflect(lightDirection, worldNormal) * uCameraRotation;
   5584 </a><a href="#h4-0-485" id="h4-0-485" class="i">+  vec2 newTexCoor = mapTextureToNormal( R );
   5585 </a><a href="#h4-0-486" id="h4-0-486" class="i">+#ifdef WEBGL2
   5586 </a><a href="#h4-0-487" id="h4-0-487" class="i">+  // In p5js the range of shininess is &gt;= 1,
   5587 </a><a href="#h4-0-488" id="h4-0-488" class="i">+  // Therefore roughness range will be ([0,1]*8)*20 or [0, 160]
   5588 </a><a href="#h4-0-489" id="h4-0-489" class="i">+  // The factor of 8 is because currently the getSpecularTexture
   5589 </a><a href="#h4-0-490" id="h4-0-490" class="i">+  // only calculated 8 different levels of roughness
   5590 </a><a href="#h4-0-491" id="h4-0-491" class="i">+  // The factor of 20 is just to spread up this range so that,
   5591 </a><a href="#h4-0-492" id="h4-0-492" class="i">+  // [1, max] of shininess is converted to [0,160] of roughness
   5592 </a><a href="#h4-0-493" id="h4-0-493" class="i">+  float roughness = 20. / shininess;
   5593 </a><a href="#h4-0-494" id="h4-0-494" class="i">+  vec4 outColor = textureLod(environmentMapSpecular, newTexCoor, roughness * 8.);
   5594 </a><a href="#h4-0-495" id="h4-0-495" class="i">+#else
   5595 </a><a href="#h4-0-496" id="h4-0-496" class="i">+  vec4 outColor = TEXTURE(environmentMapSpecular, newTexCoor);
   5596 </a><a href="#h4-0-497" id="h4-0-497" class="i">+#endif
   5597 </a><a href="#h4-0-498" id="h4-0-498" class="i">+  // this is to make the darker sections more dark
   5598 </a><a href="#h4-0-499" id="h4-0-499" class="i">+  // png and jpg usually flatten the brightness so it is to reverse that
   5599 </a><a href="#h4-0-500" id="h4-0-500" class="i">+  return mix(
   5600 </a><a href="#h4-0-501" id="h4-0-501" class="i">+    pow(outColor.xyz, vec3(10)),
   5601 </a><a href="#h4-0-502" id="h4-0-502" class="i">+    pow(outColor.xyz, vec3(1.2)),
   5602 </a><a href="#h4-0-503" id="h4-0-503" class="i">+    metallic 
   5603 </a><a href="#h4-0-504" id="h4-0-504" class="i">+  );
   5604 </a><a href="#h4-0-505" id="h4-0-505" class="i">+}
   5605 </a><a href="#h4-0-506" id="h4-0-506" class="i">+
   5606 </a><a href="#h4-0-507" id="h4-0-507" class="i">+void totalLight(
   5607 </a><a href="#h4-0-508" id="h4-0-508" class="i">+  vec3 modelPosition,
   5608 </a><a href="#h4-0-509" id="h4-0-509" class="i">+  vec3 normal,
   5609 </a><a href="#h4-0-510" id="h4-0-510" class="i">+  float shininess,
   5610 </a><a href="#h4-0-511" id="h4-0-511" class="i">+  float metallic,
   5611 </a><a href="#h4-0-512" id="h4-0-512" class="i">+  out vec3 totalDiffuse,
   5612 </a><a href="#h4-0-513" id="h4-0-513" class="i">+  out vec3 totalSpecular
   5613 </a><a href="#h4-0-514" id="h4-0-514" class="i">+) {
   5614 </a><a href="#h4-0-515" id="h4-0-515" class="i">+
   5615 </a><a href="#h4-0-516" id="h4-0-516" class="i">+  totalSpecular = vec3(0.0);
   5616 </a><a href="#h4-0-517" id="h4-0-517" class="i">+
   5617 </a><a href="#h4-0-518" id="h4-0-518" class="i">+  if (!uUseLighting) {
   5618 </a><a href="#h4-0-519" id="h4-0-519" class="i">+    totalDiffuse = vec3(1.0);
   5619 </a><a href="#h4-0-520" id="h4-0-520" class="i">+    return;
   5620 </a><a href="#h4-0-521" id="h4-0-521" class="i">+  }
   5621 </a><a href="#h4-0-522" id="h4-0-522" class="i">+
   5622 </a><a href="#h4-0-523" id="h4-0-523" class="i">+  totalDiffuse = vec3(0.0);
   5623 </a><a href="#h4-0-524" id="h4-0-524" class="i">+
   5624 </a><a href="#h4-0-525" id="h4-0-525" class="i">+  vec3 viewDirection = normalize(-modelPosition);
   5625 </a><a href="#h4-0-526" id="h4-0-526" class="i">+
   5626 </a><a href="#h4-0-527" id="h4-0-527" class="i">+  for (int j = 0; j &lt; 5; j++) {
   5627 </a><a href="#h4-0-528" id="h4-0-528" class="i">+    if (j &lt; uDirectionalLightCount) {
   5628 </a><a href="#h4-0-529" id="h4-0-529" class="i">+      vec3 lightVector = (uViewMatrix * vec4(uLightingDirection[j], 0.0)).xyz;
   5629 </a><a href="#h4-0-530" id="h4-0-530" class="i">+      vec3 lightColor = uDirectionalDiffuseColors[j];
   5630 </a><a href="#h4-0-531" id="h4-0-531" class="i">+      vec3 specularColor = uDirectionalSpecularColors[j];
   5631 </a><a href="#h4-0-532" id="h4-0-532" class="i">+      LightResult result = _light(viewDirection, normal, lightVector, shininess, metallic);
   5632 </a><a href="#h4-0-533" id="h4-0-533" class="i">+      totalDiffuse += result.diffuse * lightColor;
   5633 </a><a href="#h4-0-534" id="h4-0-534" class="i">+      totalSpecular += result.specular * lightColor * specularColor;
   5634 </a><a href="#h4-0-535" id="h4-0-535" class="i">+    }
   5635 </a><a href="#h4-0-536" id="h4-0-536" class="i">+
   5636 </a><a href="#h4-0-537" id="h4-0-537" class="i">+    if (j &lt; uPointLightCount) {
   5637 </a><a href="#h4-0-538" id="h4-0-538" class="i">+      vec3 lightPosition = (uViewMatrix * vec4(uPointLightLocation[j], 1.0)).xyz;
   5638 </a><a href="#h4-0-539" id="h4-0-539" class="i">+      vec3 lightVector = modelPosition - lightPosition;
   5639 </a><a href="#h4-0-540" id="h4-0-540" class="i">+      //calculate attenuation
   5640 </a><a href="#h4-0-541" id="h4-0-541" class="i">+      float lightDistance = length(lightVector);
   5641 </a><a href="#h4-0-542" id="h4-0-542" class="i">+      float lightFalloff = 1.0 / (uConstantAttenuation + lightDistance * uLinearAttenuation + (lightDistance * lightDistance) * uQuadraticAttenuation);
   5642 </a><a href="#h4-0-543" id="h4-0-543" class="i">+      vec3 lightColor = lightFalloff * uPointLightDiffuseColors[j];
   5643 </a><a href="#h4-0-544" id="h4-0-544" class="i">+      vec3 specularColor = lightFalloff * uPointLightSpecularColors[j];
   5644 </a><a href="#h4-0-545" id="h4-0-545" class="i">+
   5645 </a><a href="#h4-0-546" id="h4-0-546" class="i">+      LightResult result = _light(viewDirection, normal, lightVector, shininess, metallic);
   5646 </a><a href="#h4-0-547" id="h4-0-547" class="i">+      totalDiffuse += result.diffuse * lightColor;
   5647 </a><a href="#h4-0-548" id="h4-0-548" class="i">+      totalSpecular += result.specular * lightColor * specularColor;
   5648 </a><a href="#h4-0-549" id="h4-0-549" class="i">+    }
   5649 </a><a href="#h4-0-550" id="h4-0-550" class="i">+
   5650 </a><a href="#h4-0-551" id="h4-0-551" class="i">+    if(j &lt; uSpotLightCount) {
   5651 </a><a href="#h4-0-552" id="h4-0-552" class="i">+      vec3 lightPosition = (uViewMatrix * vec4(uSpotLightLocation[j], 1.0)).xyz;
   5652 </a><a href="#h4-0-553" id="h4-0-553" class="i">+      vec3 lightVector = modelPosition - lightPosition;
   5653 </a><a href="#h4-0-554" id="h4-0-554" class="i">+    
   5654 </a><a href="#h4-0-555" id="h4-0-555" class="i">+      float lightDistance = length(lightVector);
   5655 </a><a href="#h4-0-556" id="h4-0-556" class="i">+      float lightFalloff = 1.0 / (uConstantAttenuation + lightDistance * uLinearAttenuation + (lightDistance * lightDistance) * uQuadraticAttenuation);
   5656 </a><a href="#h4-0-557" id="h4-0-557" class="i">+
   5657 </a><a href="#h4-0-558" id="h4-0-558" class="i">+      vec3 lightDirection = (uViewMatrix * vec4(uSpotLightDirection[j], 0.0)).xyz;
   5658 </a><a href="#h4-0-559" id="h4-0-559" class="i">+      float spotDot = dot(normalize(lightVector), normalize(lightDirection));
   5659 </a><a href="#h4-0-560" id="h4-0-560" class="i">+      float spotFalloff;
   5660 </a><a href="#h4-0-561" id="h4-0-561" class="i">+      if(spotDot &lt; uSpotLightAngle[j]) {
   5661 </a><a href="#h4-0-562" id="h4-0-562" class="i">+        spotFalloff = 0.0;
   5662 </a><a href="#h4-0-563" id="h4-0-563" class="i">+      }
   5663 </a><a href="#h4-0-564" id="h4-0-564" class="i">+      else {
   5664 </a><a href="#h4-0-565" id="h4-0-565" class="i">+        spotFalloff = pow(spotDot, uSpotLightConc[j]);
   5665 </a><a href="#h4-0-566" id="h4-0-566" class="i">+      }
   5666 </a><a href="#h4-0-567" id="h4-0-567" class="i">+      lightFalloff *= spotFalloff;
   5667 </a><a href="#h4-0-568" id="h4-0-568" class="i">+
   5668 </a><a href="#h4-0-569" id="h4-0-569" class="i">+      vec3 lightColor = uSpotLightDiffuseColors[j];
   5669 </a><a href="#h4-0-570" id="h4-0-570" class="i">+      vec3 specularColor = uSpotLightSpecularColors[j];
   5670 </a><a href="#h4-0-571" id="h4-0-571" class="i">+     
   5671 </a><a href="#h4-0-572" id="h4-0-572" class="i">+      LightResult result = _light(viewDirection, normal, lightVector, shininess, metallic);
   5672 </a><a href="#h4-0-573" id="h4-0-573" class="i">+      
   5673 </a><a href="#h4-0-574" id="h4-0-574" class="i">+      totalDiffuse += result.diffuse * lightColor * lightFalloff;
   5674 </a><a href="#h4-0-575" id="h4-0-575" class="i">+      totalSpecular += result.specular * lightColor * specularColor * lightFalloff;
   5675 </a><a href="#h4-0-576" id="h4-0-576" class="i">+    }
   5676 </a><a href="#h4-0-577" id="h4-0-577" class="i">+  }
   5677 </a><a href="#h4-0-578" id="h4-0-578" class="i">+
   5678 </a><a href="#h4-0-579" id="h4-0-579" class="i">+  if( uUseImageLight ){
   5679 </a><a href="#h4-0-580" id="h4-0-580" class="i">+    totalDiffuse += calculateImageDiffuse(normal, modelPosition, metallic);
   5680 </a><a href="#h4-0-581" id="h4-0-581" class="i">+    totalSpecular += calculateImageSpecular(normal, modelPosition, shininess, metallic);
   5681 </a><a href="#h4-0-582" id="h4-0-582" class="i">+  }
   5682 </a><a href="#h4-0-583" id="h4-0-583" class="i">+
   5683 </a><a href="#h4-0-584" id="h4-0-584" class="i">+  totalDiffuse *= diffuseFactor;
   5684 </a><a href="#h4-0-585" id="h4-0-585" class="i">+  totalSpecular *= specularFactor;
   5685 </a><a href="#h4-0-586" id="h4-0-586" class="i">+}
   5686 </a><a href="#h4-0-587" id="h4-0-587" class="i">+`,ol=`#ifdef WEBGL2
   5687 </a><a href="#h4-0-588" id="h4-0-588" class="i">+
   5688 </a><a href="#h4-0-589" id="h4-0-589" class="i">+#define IN in
   5689 </a><a href="#h4-0-590" id="h4-0-590" class="i">+#define OUT out
   5690 </a><a href="#h4-0-591" id="h4-0-591" class="i">+
   5691 </a><a href="#h4-0-592" id="h4-0-592" class="i">+#ifdef FRAGMENT_SHADER
   5692 </a><a href="#h4-0-593" id="h4-0-593" class="i">+out vec4 outColor;
   5693 </a><a href="#h4-0-594" id="h4-0-594" class="i">+#define OUT_COLOR outColor
   5694 </a><a href="#h4-0-595" id="h4-0-595" class="i">+#endif
   5695 </a><a href="#h4-0-596" id="h4-0-596" class="i">+#define TEXTURE texture
   5696 </a><a href="#h4-0-597" id="h4-0-597" class="i">+
   5697 </a><a href="#h4-0-598" id="h4-0-598" class="i">+#else
   5698 </a><a href="#h4-0-599" id="h4-0-599" class="i">+
   5699 </a><a href="#h4-0-600" id="h4-0-600" class="i">+#ifdef FRAGMENT_SHADER
   5700 </a><a href="#h4-0-601" id="h4-0-601" class="i">+#define IN varying
   5701 </a><a href="#h4-0-602" id="h4-0-602" class="i">+#else
   5702 </a><a href="#h4-0-603" id="h4-0-603" class="i">+#define IN attribute
   5703 </a><a href="#h4-0-604" id="h4-0-604" class="i">+#endif
   5704 </a><a href="#h4-0-605" id="h4-0-605" class="i">+#define OUT varying
   5705 </a><a href="#h4-0-606" id="h4-0-606" class="i">+#define TEXTURE texture2D
   5706 </a><a href="#h4-0-607" id="h4-0-607" class="i">+
   5707 </a><a href="#h4-0-608" id="h4-0-608" class="i">+#ifdef FRAGMENT_SHADER
   5708 </a><a href="#h4-0-609" id="h4-0-609" class="i">+#define OUT_COLOR gl_FragColor
   5709 </a><a href="#h4-0-610" id="h4-0-610" class="i">+#endif
   5710 </a><a href="#h4-0-611" id="h4-0-611" class="i">+
   5711 </a><a href="#h4-0-612" id="h4-0-612" class="i">+#endif
   5712 </a><a href="#h4-0-613" id="h4-0-613" class="i">+
   5713 </a><a href="#h4-0-614" id="h4-0-614" class="i">+#ifdef FRAGMENT_SHADER
   5714 </a><a href="#h4-0-615" id="h4-0-615" class="i">+vec4 getTexture(in sampler2D content, vec2 coord) {
   5715 </a><a href="#h4-0-616" id="h4-0-616" class="i">+  vec4 color = TEXTURE(content, coord);
   5716 </a><a href="#h4-0-617" id="h4-0-617" class="i">+  color.rgb /= color.a;
   5717 </a><a href="#h4-0-618" id="h4-0-618" class="i">+  return color;
   5718 </a><a href="#h4-0-619" id="h4-0-619" class="i">+}
   5719 </a><a href="#h4-0-620" id="h4-0-620" class="i">+#endif
   5720 </a><a href="#h4-0-621" id="h4-0-621" class="i">+`,vb=`IN vec3 aPosition;
   5721 </a><a href="#h4-0-622" id="h4-0-622" class="i">+IN vec3 aNormal;
   5722 </a><a href="#h4-0-623" id="h4-0-623" class="i">+IN vec2 aTexCoord;
   5723 </a><a href="#h4-0-624" id="h4-0-624" class="i">+IN vec4 aVertexColor;
   5724 </a><a href="#h4-0-625" id="h4-0-625" class="i">+
   5725 </a><a href="#h4-0-626" id="h4-0-626" class="i">+#define HOOK_DEFINES
   5726 </a><a href="#h4-0-627" id="h4-0-627" class="i">+
   5727 </a><a href="#h4-0-628" id="h4-0-628" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getWorldInputs
   5728 </a><a href="#h4-0-629" id="h4-0-629" class="i">+uniform mat4 uModelMatrix;
   5729 </a><a href="#h4-0-630" id="h4-0-630" class="i">+uniform mat4 uViewMatrix;
   5730 </a><a href="#h4-0-631" id="h4-0-631" class="i">+uniform mat3 uModelNormalMatrix;
   5731 </a><a href="#h4-0-632" id="h4-0-632" class="i">+uniform mat3 uCameraNormalMatrix;
   5732 </a><a href="#h4-0-633" id="h4-0-633" class="i">+#else
   5733 </a><a href="#h4-0-634" id="h4-0-634" class="i">+uniform mat4 uModelViewMatrix;
   5734 </a><a href="#h4-0-635" id="h4-0-635" class="i">+uniform mat3 uNormalMatrix;
   5735 </a><a href="#h4-0-636" id="h4-0-636" class="i">+#endif
   5736 </a><a href="#h4-0-637" id="h4-0-637" class="i">+uniform mat4 uProjectionMatrix;
   5737 </a><a href="#h4-0-638" id="h4-0-638" class="i">+
   5738 </a><a href="#h4-0-639" id="h4-0-639" class="i">+uniform vec4 uMaterialColor;
   5739 </a><a href="#h4-0-640" id="h4-0-640" class="i">+uniform bool uUseVertexColor;
   5740 </a><a href="#h4-0-641" id="h4-0-641" class="i">+
   5741 </a><a href="#h4-0-642" id="h4-0-642" class="i">+OUT vec3 vVertexNormal;
   5742 </a><a href="#h4-0-643" id="h4-0-643" class="i">+OUT highp vec2 vVertTexCoord;
   5743 </a><a href="#h4-0-644" id="h4-0-644" class="i">+OUT vec4 vColor;
   5744 </a><a href="#h4-0-645" id="h4-0-645" class="i">+
   5745 </a><a href="#h4-0-646" id="h4-0-646" class="i">+struct Vertex {
   5746 </a><a href="#h4-0-647" id="h4-0-647" class="i">+  vec3 position;
   5747 </a><a href="#h4-0-648" id="h4-0-648" class="i">+  vec3 normal;
   5748 </a><a href="#h4-0-649" id="h4-0-649" class="i">+  vec2 texCoord;
   5749 </a><a href="#h4-0-650" id="h4-0-650" class="i">+  vec4 color;
   5750 </a><a href="#h4-0-651" id="h4-0-651" class="i">+};
   5751 </a><a href="#h4-0-652" id="h4-0-652" class="i">+
   5752 </a><a href="#h4-0-653" id="h4-0-653" class="i">+void main(void) {
   5753 </a><a href="#h4-0-654" id="h4-0-654" class="i">+  HOOK_beforeVertex();
   5754 </a><a href="#h4-0-655" id="h4-0-655" class="i">+
   5755 </a><a href="#h4-0-656" id="h4-0-656" class="i">+  Vertex inputs;
   5756 </a><a href="#h4-0-657" id="h4-0-657" class="i">+  inputs.position = aPosition;
   5757 </a><a href="#h4-0-658" id="h4-0-658" class="i">+  inputs.normal = aNormal;
   5758 </a><a href="#h4-0-659" id="h4-0-659" class="i">+  inputs.texCoord = aTexCoord;
   5759 </a><a href="#h4-0-660" id="h4-0-660" class="i">+  inputs.color = (uUseVertexColor &amp;&amp; aVertexColor.x &gt;= 0.0) ? aVertexColor : uMaterialColor;
   5760 </a><a href="#h4-0-661" id="h4-0-661" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getObjectInputs
   5761 </a><a href="#h4-0-662" id="h4-0-662" class="i">+  inputs = HOOK_getObjectInputs(inputs);
   5762 </a><a href="#h4-0-663" id="h4-0-663" class="i">+#endif
   5763 </a><a href="#h4-0-664" id="h4-0-664" class="i">+
   5764 </a><a href="#h4-0-665" id="h4-0-665" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getWorldInputs
   5765 </a><a href="#h4-0-666" id="h4-0-666" class="i">+  inputs.position = (uModelMatrix * vec4(inputs.position, 1.)).xyz;
   5766 </a><a href="#h4-0-667" id="h4-0-667" class="i">+  inputs.normal = uModelNormalMatrix * inputs.normal;
   5767 </a><a href="#h4-0-668" id="h4-0-668" class="i">+  inputs = HOOK_getWorldInputs(inputs);
   5768 </a><a href="#h4-0-669" id="h4-0-669" class="i">+#endif
   5769 </a><a href="#h4-0-670" id="h4-0-670" class="i">+
   5770 </a><a href="#h4-0-671" id="h4-0-671" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getWorldInputs
   5771 </a><a href="#h4-0-672" id="h4-0-672" class="i">+  // Already multiplied by the model matrix, just apply view
   5772 </a><a href="#h4-0-673" id="h4-0-673" class="i">+  inputs.position = (uViewMatrix * vec4(inputs.position, 1.)).xyz;
   5773 </a><a href="#h4-0-674" id="h4-0-674" class="i">+  inputs.normal = uCameraNormalMatrix * inputs.normal;
   5774 </a><a href="#h4-0-675" id="h4-0-675" class="i">+#else
   5775 </a><a href="#h4-0-676" id="h4-0-676" class="i">+  // Apply both at once
   5776 </a><a href="#h4-0-677" id="h4-0-677" class="i">+  inputs.position = (uModelViewMatrix * vec4(inputs.position, 1.)).xyz;
   5777 </a><a href="#h4-0-678" id="h4-0-678" class="i">+  inputs.normal = uNormalMatrix * inputs.normal;
   5778 </a><a href="#h4-0-679" id="h4-0-679" class="i">+#endif
   5779 </a><a href="#h4-0-680" id="h4-0-680" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getCameraInputs
   5780 </a><a href="#h4-0-681" id="h4-0-681" class="i">+  inputs = HOOK_getCameraInputs(inputs);
   5781 </a><a href="#h4-0-682" id="h4-0-682" class="i">+#endif
   5782 </a><a href="#h4-0-683" id="h4-0-683" class="i">+
   5783 </a><a href="#h4-0-684" id="h4-0-684" class="i">+  // Pass varyings to fragment shader
   5784 </a><a href="#h4-0-685" id="h4-0-685" class="i">+  vVertTexCoord = inputs.texCoord;
   5785 </a><a href="#h4-0-686" id="h4-0-686" class="i">+  vVertexNormal = normalize(inputs.normal);
   5786 </a><a href="#h4-0-687" id="h4-0-687" class="i">+  vColor = inputs.color;
   5787 </a><a href="#h4-0-688" id="h4-0-688" class="i">+
   5788 </a><a href="#h4-0-689" id="h4-0-689" class="i">+  gl_Position = uProjectionMatrix * vec4(inputs.position, 1.);
   5789 </a><a href="#h4-0-690" id="h4-0-690" class="i">+
   5790 </a><a href="#h4-0-691" id="h4-0-691" class="i">+  HOOK_afterVertex();
   5791 </a><a href="#h4-0-692" id="h4-0-692" class="i">+}
   5792 </a><a href="#h4-0-693" id="h4-0-693" class="i">+`,xb=`IN vec3 vVertexNormal;
   5793 </a><a href="#h4-0-694" id="h4-0-694" class="i">+void main(void) {
   5794 </a><a href="#h4-0-695" id="h4-0-695" class="i">+  HOOK_beforeFragment();
   5795 </a><a href="#h4-0-696" id="h4-0-696" class="i">+  OUT_COLOR = HOOK_getFinalColor(vec4(vVertexNormal, 1.0));
   5796 </a><a href="#h4-0-697" id="h4-0-697" class="i">+  HOOK_afterFragment();
   5797 </a><a href="#h4-0-698" id="h4-0-698" class="i">+}
   5798 </a><a href="#h4-0-699" id="h4-0-699" class="i">+`,bb=`IN vec4 vColor;
   5799 </a><a href="#h4-0-700" id="h4-0-700" class="i">+void main(void) {
   5800 </a><a href="#h4-0-701" id="h4-0-701" class="i">+  HOOK_beforeFragment();
   5801 </a><a href="#h4-0-702" id="h4-0-702" class="i">+  OUT_COLOR = HOOK_getFinalColor(vec4(vColor.rgb, 1.) * vColor.a);
   5802 </a><a href="#h4-0-703" id="h4-0-703" class="i">+  HOOK_afterFragment();
   5803 </a><a href="#h4-0-704" id="h4-0-704" class="i">+}
   5804 </a><a href="#h4-0-705" id="h4-0-705" class="i">+`,_b=`#define PI 3.141592
   5805 </a><a href="#h4-0-706" id="h4-0-706" class="i">+
   5806 </a><a href="#h4-0-707" id="h4-0-707" class="i">+precision highp float;
   5807 </a><a href="#h4-0-708" id="h4-0-708" class="i">+  
   5808 </a><a href="#h4-0-709" id="h4-0-709" class="i">+uniform sampler2D uEnvMap;
   5809 </a><a href="#h4-0-710" id="h4-0-710" class="i">+uniform mat3 uNewNormalMatrix;
   5810 </a><a href="#h4-0-711" id="h4-0-711" class="i">+uniform float uFovY;
   5811 </a><a href="#h4-0-712" id="h4-0-712" class="i">+uniform float uAspect;
   5812 </a><a href="#h4-0-713" id="h4-0-713" class="i">+
   5813 </a><a href="#h4-0-714" id="h4-0-714" class="i">+varying vec2 vTexCoord;
   5814 </a><a href="#h4-0-715" id="h4-0-715" class="i">+  
   5815 </a><a href="#h4-0-716" id="h4-0-716" class="i">+void main() {
   5816 </a><a href="#h4-0-717" id="h4-0-717" class="i">+    float uFovX = uFovY * uAspect; 
   5817 </a><a href="#h4-0-718" id="h4-0-718" class="i">+    float angleY = mix(uFovY/2.0,  -uFovY/2.0, vTexCoord.y);
   5818 </a><a href="#h4-0-719" id="h4-0-719" class="i">+    float angleX = mix(uFovX/2.0, -uFovX/2.0, vTexCoord.x);
   5819 </a><a href="#h4-0-720" id="h4-0-720" class="i">+    vec3 rotatedNormal = vec3( angleX, angleY, 1.0 );
   5820 </a><a href="#h4-0-721" id="h4-0-721" class="i">+    rotatedNormal = uNewNormalMatrix * normalize(rotatedNormal);
   5821 </a><a href="#h4-0-722" id="h4-0-722" class="i">+    float temp = rotatedNormal.z;
   5822 </a><a href="#h4-0-723" id="h4-0-723" class="i">+    rotatedNormal.z = rotatedNormal.x;
   5823 </a><a href="#h4-0-724" id="h4-0-724" class="i">+    rotatedNormal.x = -temp;
   5824 </a><a href="#h4-0-725" id="h4-0-725" class="i">+    vec2 suv;
   5825 </a><a href="#h4-0-726" id="h4-0-726" class="i">+    suv.y = 0.5 + 0.5 * (-rotatedNormal.y);
   5826 </a><a href="#h4-0-727" id="h4-0-727" class="i">+    suv.x = atan(rotatedNormal.z, rotatedNormal.x) / (2.0 * PI) + 0.5;
   5827 </a><a href="#h4-0-728" id="h4-0-728" class="i">+    vec4 newTexColor = texture2D(uEnvMap, suv.xy);
   5828 </a><a href="#h4-0-729" id="h4-0-729" class="i">+    gl_FragColor = newTexColor;
   5829 </a><a href="#h4-0-730" id="h4-0-730" class="i">+}
   5830 </a><a href="#h4-0-731" id="h4-0-731" class="i">+`,wb=`// include lighting.glgl
   5831 </a><a href="#h4-0-732" id="h4-0-732" class="i">+
   5832 </a><a href="#h4-0-733" id="h4-0-733" class="i">+IN vec3 aPosition;
   5833 </a><a href="#h4-0-734" id="h4-0-734" class="i">+IN vec3 aNormal;
   5834 </a><a href="#h4-0-735" id="h4-0-735" class="i">+IN vec2 aTexCoord;
   5835 </a><a href="#h4-0-736" id="h4-0-736" class="i">+IN vec4 aVertexColor;
   5836 </a><a href="#h4-0-737" id="h4-0-737" class="i">+
   5837 </a><a href="#h4-0-738" id="h4-0-738" class="i">+uniform mat4 uModelViewMatrix;
   5838 </a><a href="#h4-0-739" id="h4-0-739" class="i">+uniform mat4 uProjectionMatrix;
   5839 </a><a href="#h4-0-740" id="h4-0-740" class="i">+uniform mat3 uNormalMatrix;
   5840 </a><a href="#h4-0-741" id="h4-0-741" class="i">+
   5841 </a><a href="#h4-0-742" id="h4-0-742" class="i">+uniform bool uUseVertexColor;
   5842 </a><a href="#h4-0-743" id="h4-0-743" class="i">+uniform vec4 uMaterialColor;
   5843 </a><a href="#h4-0-744" id="h4-0-744" class="i">+
   5844 </a><a href="#h4-0-745" id="h4-0-745" class="i">+OUT highp vec2 vVertTexCoord;
   5845 </a><a href="#h4-0-746" id="h4-0-746" class="i">+OUT vec3 vDiffuseColor;
   5846 </a><a href="#h4-0-747" id="h4-0-747" class="i">+OUT vec3 vSpecularColor;
   5847 </a><a href="#h4-0-748" id="h4-0-748" class="i">+OUT vec4 vColor;
   5848 </a><a href="#h4-0-749" id="h4-0-749" class="i">+
   5849 </a><a href="#h4-0-750" id="h4-0-750" class="i">+void main(void) {
   5850 </a><a href="#h4-0-751" id="h4-0-751" class="i">+
   5851 </a><a href="#h4-0-752" id="h4-0-752" class="i">+  vec4 viewModelPosition = uModelViewMatrix * vec4(aPosition, 1.0);
   5852 </a><a href="#h4-0-753" id="h4-0-753" class="i">+  gl_Position = uProjectionMatrix * viewModelPosition;
   5853 </a><a href="#h4-0-754" id="h4-0-754" class="i">+
   5854 </a><a href="#h4-0-755" id="h4-0-755" class="i">+  vec3 vertexNormal = normalize(uNormalMatrix * aNormal);
   5855 </a><a href="#h4-0-756" id="h4-0-756" class="i">+  vVertTexCoord = aTexCoord;
   5856 </a><a href="#h4-0-757" id="h4-0-757" class="i">+
   5857 </a><a href="#h4-0-758" id="h4-0-758" class="i">+  totalLight(viewModelPosition.xyz, vertexNormal, vDiffuseColor, vSpecularColor);
   5858 </a><a href="#h4-0-759" id="h4-0-759" class="i">+
   5859 </a><a href="#h4-0-760" id="h4-0-760" class="i">+  for (int i = 0; i &lt; 8; i++) {
   5860 </a><a href="#h4-0-761" id="h4-0-761" class="i">+    if (i &lt; uAmbientLightCount) {
   5861 </a><a href="#h4-0-762" id="h4-0-762" class="i">+      vDiffuseColor += uAmbientColor[i];
   5862 </a><a href="#h4-0-763" id="h4-0-763" class="i">+    }
   5863 </a><a href="#h4-0-764" id="h4-0-764" class="i">+  }
   5864 </a><a href="#h4-0-765" id="h4-0-765" class="i">+  
   5865 </a><a href="#h4-0-766" id="h4-0-766" class="i">+  vColor = ((uUseVertexColor &amp;&amp; aVertexColor.x &gt;= 0.0) ? aVertexColor : uMaterialColor);
   5866 </a><a href="#h4-0-767" id="h4-0-767" class="i">+}
   5867 </a><a href="#h4-0-768" id="h4-0-768" class="i">+`,Cb=`uniform vec4 uTint;
   5868 </a><a href="#h4-0-769" id="h4-0-769" class="i">+uniform sampler2D uSampler;
   5869 </a><a href="#h4-0-770" id="h4-0-770" class="i">+uniform bool isTexture;
   5870 </a><a href="#h4-0-771" id="h4-0-771" class="i">+uniform bool uEmissive;
   5871 </a><a href="#h4-0-772" id="h4-0-772" class="i">+
   5872 </a><a href="#h4-0-773" id="h4-0-773" class="i">+IN highp vec2 vVertTexCoord;
   5873 </a><a href="#h4-0-774" id="h4-0-774" class="i">+IN vec3 vDiffuseColor;
   5874 </a><a href="#h4-0-775" id="h4-0-775" class="i">+IN vec3 vSpecularColor;
   5875 </a><a href="#h4-0-776" id="h4-0-776" class="i">+IN vec4 vColor;
   5876 </a><a href="#h4-0-777" id="h4-0-777" class="i">+
   5877 </a><a href="#h4-0-778" id="h4-0-778" class="i">+void main(void) {
   5878 </a><a href="#h4-0-779" id="h4-0-779" class="i">+  if(uEmissive &amp;&amp; !isTexture) {
   5879 </a><a href="#h4-0-780" id="h4-0-780" class="i">+    OUT_COLOR = vColor;
   5880 </a><a href="#h4-0-781" id="h4-0-781" class="i">+  }
   5881 </a><a href="#h4-0-782" id="h4-0-782" class="i">+  else {
   5882 </a><a href="#h4-0-783" id="h4-0-783" class="i">+    vec4 baseColor = isTexture
   5883 </a><a href="#h4-0-784" id="h4-0-784" class="i">+      // Textures come in with premultiplied alpha. To apply tint and still have
   5884 </a><a href="#h4-0-785" id="h4-0-785" class="i">+      // premultiplied alpha output, we need to multiply the RGB channels by the
   5885 </a><a href="#h4-0-786" id="h4-0-786" class="i">+      // tint RGB, and all channels by the tint alpha.
   5886 </a><a href="#h4-0-787" id="h4-0-787" class="i">+      ? TEXTURE(uSampler, vVertTexCoord) * vec4(uTint.rgb/255., 1.) * (uTint.a/255.)
   5887 </a><a href="#h4-0-788" id="h4-0-788" class="i">+      // Colors come in with unmultiplied alpha, so we need to multiply the RGB
   5888 </a><a href="#h4-0-789" id="h4-0-789" class="i">+      // channels by alpha to convert it to premultiplied alpha.
   5889 </a><a href="#h4-0-790" id="h4-0-790" class="i">+      : vec4(vColor.rgb * vColor.a, vColor.a);
   5890 </a><a href="#h4-0-791" id="h4-0-791" class="i">+    OUT_COLOR = vec4(baseColor.rgb * vDiffuseColor + vSpecularColor, baseColor.a);
   5891 </a><a href="#h4-0-792" id="h4-0-792" class="i">+  }
   5892 </a><a href="#h4-0-793" id="h4-0-793" class="i">+}
   5893 </a><a href="#h4-0-794" id="h4-0-794" class="i">+`,Eb=`precision highp int;
   5894 </a><a href="#h4-0-795" id="h4-0-795" class="i">+
   5895 </a><a href="#h4-0-796" id="h4-0-796" class="i">+#define HOOK_DEFINES
   5896 </a><a href="#h4-0-797" id="h4-0-797" class="i">+
   5897 </a><a href="#h4-0-798" id="h4-0-798" class="i">+IN vec3 aPosition;
   5898 </a><a href="#h4-0-799" id="h4-0-799" class="i">+IN vec3 aNormal;
   5899 </a><a href="#h4-0-800" id="h4-0-800" class="i">+IN vec2 aTexCoord;
   5900 </a><a href="#h4-0-801" id="h4-0-801" class="i">+IN vec4 aVertexColor;
   5901 </a><a href="#h4-0-802" id="h4-0-802" class="i">+
   5902 </a><a href="#h4-0-803" id="h4-0-803" class="i">+uniform vec3 uAmbientColor[5];
   5903 </a><a href="#h4-0-804" id="h4-0-804" class="i">+
   5904 </a><a href="#h4-0-805" id="h4-0-805" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getWorldInputs
   5905 </a><a href="#h4-0-806" id="h4-0-806" class="i">+uniform mat4 uModelMatrix;
   5906 </a><a href="#h4-0-807" id="h4-0-807" class="i">+uniform mat4 uViewMatrix;
   5907 </a><a href="#h4-0-808" id="h4-0-808" class="i">+uniform mat3 uModelNormalMatrix;
   5908 </a><a href="#h4-0-809" id="h4-0-809" class="i">+uniform mat3 uCameraNormalMatrix;
   5909 </a><a href="#h4-0-810" id="h4-0-810" class="i">+#else
   5910 </a><a href="#h4-0-811" id="h4-0-811" class="i">+uniform mat4 uModelViewMatrix;
   5911 </a><a href="#h4-0-812" id="h4-0-812" class="i">+uniform mat3 uNormalMatrix;
   5912 </a><a href="#h4-0-813" id="h4-0-813" class="i">+#endif
   5913 </a><a href="#h4-0-814" id="h4-0-814" class="i">+uniform mat4 uProjectionMatrix;
   5914 </a><a href="#h4-0-815" id="h4-0-815" class="i">+uniform int uAmbientLightCount;
   5915 </a><a href="#h4-0-816" id="h4-0-816" class="i">+
   5916 </a><a href="#h4-0-817" id="h4-0-817" class="i">+uniform bool uUseVertexColor;
   5917 </a><a href="#h4-0-818" id="h4-0-818" class="i">+uniform vec4 uMaterialColor;
   5918 </a><a href="#h4-0-819" id="h4-0-819" class="i">+
   5919 </a><a href="#h4-0-820" id="h4-0-820" class="i">+OUT vec3 vNormal;
   5920 </a><a href="#h4-0-821" id="h4-0-821" class="i">+OUT vec2 vTexCoord;
   5921 </a><a href="#h4-0-822" id="h4-0-822" class="i">+OUT vec3 vViewPosition;
   5922 </a><a href="#h4-0-823" id="h4-0-823" class="i">+OUT vec3 vAmbientColor;
   5923 </a><a href="#h4-0-824" id="h4-0-824" class="i">+OUT vec4 vColor;
   5924 </a><a href="#h4-0-825" id="h4-0-825" class="i">+
   5925 </a><a href="#h4-0-826" id="h4-0-826" class="i">+struct Vertex {
   5926 </a><a href="#h4-0-827" id="h4-0-827" class="i">+  vec3 position;
   5927 </a><a href="#h4-0-828" id="h4-0-828" class="i">+  vec3 normal;
   5928 </a><a href="#h4-0-829" id="h4-0-829" class="i">+  vec2 texCoord;
   5929 </a><a href="#h4-0-830" id="h4-0-830" class="i">+  vec4 color;
   5930 </a><a href="#h4-0-831" id="h4-0-831" class="i">+};
   5931 </a><a href="#h4-0-832" id="h4-0-832" class="i">+
   5932 </a><a href="#h4-0-833" id="h4-0-833" class="i">+void main(void) {
   5933 </a><a href="#h4-0-834" id="h4-0-834" class="i">+  HOOK_beforeVertex();
   5934 </a><a href="#h4-0-835" id="h4-0-835" class="i">+
   5935 </a><a href="#h4-0-836" id="h4-0-836" class="i">+  Vertex inputs;
   5936 </a><a href="#h4-0-837" id="h4-0-837" class="i">+  inputs.position = aPosition;
   5937 </a><a href="#h4-0-838" id="h4-0-838" class="i">+  inputs.normal = aNormal;
   5938 </a><a href="#h4-0-839" id="h4-0-839" class="i">+  inputs.texCoord = aTexCoord;
   5939 </a><a href="#h4-0-840" id="h4-0-840" class="i">+  inputs.color = (uUseVertexColor &amp;&amp; aVertexColor.x &gt;= 0.0) ? aVertexColor : uMaterialColor;
   5940 </a><a href="#h4-0-841" id="h4-0-841" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getObjectInputs
   5941 </a><a href="#h4-0-842" id="h4-0-842" class="i">+  inputs = HOOK_getObjectInputs(inputs);
   5942 </a><a href="#h4-0-843" id="h4-0-843" class="i">+#endif
   5943 </a><a href="#h4-0-844" id="h4-0-844" class="i">+
   5944 </a><a href="#h4-0-845" id="h4-0-845" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getWorldInputs
   5945 </a><a href="#h4-0-846" id="h4-0-846" class="i">+  inputs.position = (uModelMatrix * vec4(inputs.position, 1.)).xyz;
   5946 </a><a href="#h4-0-847" id="h4-0-847" class="i">+  inputs.normal = uModelNormalMatrix * inputs.normal;
   5947 </a><a href="#h4-0-848" id="h4-0-848" class="i">+  inputs = HOOK_getWorldInputs(inputs);
   5948 </a><a href="#h4-0-849" id="h4-0-849" class="i">+#endif
   5949 </a><a href="#h4-0-850" id="h4-0-850" class="i">+
   5950 </a><a href="#h4-0-851" id="h4-0-851" class="i">+#ifdef AUGMENTED_HOOK_getWorldInputs
   5951 </a><a href="#h4-0-852" id="h4-0-852" class="i">+  // Already multiplied by the model matrix, just apply view
